race-in-madhya-pradesh-show-very-early-leads-4628251%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20opposition%20Congress%20were%20neck-and-neck%20in%20very%20early%20leads%20as%20counting%20of%20votes%20began%20-%20with%20postal%20ballots%20first%20to%20be%20opened%20for%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20election%20on%20Sunday%20morning.%20At%208.30%20am%2C%20both%20parties%20were%20tied%20at%2011%20lea%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-results-neck-and-neck-race-in-madhya-pradesh-show-very-early-leads-4628251%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-results-neck-and-neck-race-in-madhya-pradesh-show-very-early-leads-4628251%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-results-neck-and-neck-race-in-madhya-pradesh-show-very-early-leads-4628251%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tsunami%20Alert%20Lifted%20By%20Philippines%20After%207.4%20Magnitude%20Earthquake%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Philippines%20lifted%20a%20tsunami%20alert%20early%20on%20Sunday%20as%20waves%20receded%20from%20a%20magnitude%207.4%20earthquake%20that%20struck%20the%20south%20of%20the%20country%2C%20triggering%20coastal%20evacuations%20and%20some%20waves%20in%20there%20and%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20initial%20reports%20of%20casualties%20or%20serious%20damage%20from%20the%20quake%20in%20the%20Mindanao%20region%2C%20although%20some%20residents%20reported%20damage%20to%20buildings%20in%20the%20area%2C%20which%20is%20less%20populated%20than%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20archipelago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20500%20aftershocks%20were%20recorded%2C%20and%20the%20Philippines'%20Institute%20of%20Volcanology%20and%20Seismology%20(Phivolcs)%20urged%20caution%20as%20people%20resumed%20normal%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tsunami%20threat%20associated%20with%20this%20earthquake%20has%20now%20largely%20passed%20the%20Philippines%2C%26quot%3B%20Phivolcs%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20but%20advised%20people%20in%20threatened%20communities%20to%20heed%20the%20instructions%20from%20local%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20earlier%20urged%20people%20living%20near%20the%20coast%20of%20Surigao%20Del%20Sur%20and%20Davao%20Oriental%20provinces%20to%20move%20inland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20disaster%20said%20it%20was%20assessing%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20quake%2C%20with%20a%20team%20on%20the%20ground%20collating%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Philippine%20Coast%20Guard%20put%20all%20its%20vessels%20and%20aircraft%20on%20alert%20for%20potential%20dispatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20going%20back%20to%20our%20homes%20early%20on%20Sunday%2C%20although%20we%20are%20still%20shaking%20because%20of%20aftershocks%2C%26quot%3B%20Julita%20Bicap%2C%2051%2C%20a%20front%20desk%20staffer%20at%20GLC%20Suites%20hotel%20in%20the%20seaside%20town%20of%20Bislig%2C%20said%20after%20power%20was%20restored%20around%205%20a.m.%20(2100%20GMT)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20aftershocks%20even%20now.%20Last%20night%20we%20were%20at%20the%20evacuation%20centre%20including%20my%20two%20foreigner%20guests.%20One%20of%20them%20came%20back%20to%20the%20hotel%20already%2C%26quot%3B%20Bicap%20told%20Reuters%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20noticed%20a%20small%20crack%20in%20the%20hotel's%20front%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%20aftershock%20was%20magnitude%206.5%2C%20according%20to%20the%20European-Mediterranean%20Seismological%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarthquakes%20are%20common%20in%20the%20Philippines%2C%20which%20lies%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BRing%20of%20Fire%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20belt%20of%20volcanoes%20circling%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20that%20is%20prone%20to%20seismic%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScores%20of%20residents%20were%20seen%20in%20an%20evacuation%20centre%20in%20photographs%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20by%20the%20authorities%20in%20Hinatuan%20province%2C%2030%20km%20(20%20miles)%20from%20the%20quake's%20epicentre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhilvolcs'%20Hinatuan-Bislig%20Bay%20station%20recorded%20maximum%20waves%20of%200.64%20metre%20(2%20feet).%20Japan's%20Hachijojima%20island%2C%20some%20290%20km%20(180%20miles)%20south%20of%20Tokyo%2C%20recorded%20waves%20of%2040%20cm%20(1.3%20feet)%2C%20the%20Japan%20Meteorological%20Agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20Tsunami%20Warning%20System%20had%20initially%20warned%20of%20waves%20of%20up%20to%203%20metres%20(10%20feet)%20above%20the%20usual%20high%20tide%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quake%2C%20which%20struck%20at%2010%3A37%20p.m.%20(1437%20GMT)%20on%20Saturday%2C%20was%20at%20a%20depth%20of%2025%20km%20(15%20miles)%2C%20Philvolcs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJames%20Soria%2C%20who%20owns%20a%20small%20hotel%20in%20Hinatuan%2C%20said%20there%20had%20been%20significant%20damage%20to%20his%20home.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20shaking%20again%20here%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Reuters%20before%20the%20call%20was%20disconnected%20as%20another%20aftershock%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECosme%20Calejesan%2C%2047%2C%20said%20there%20had%20been%20damage%20to%20his%20house%20in%20Surigao%20City%20185%20km%20(115%20miles)%20from%20the%20epicentre%2C%20but%20the%20structure%20was%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20already%20asleep%2C%20but%20I%20was%20woken%20up%20by%20the%20creaking%20sounds%20of%20my%20cabinets%20when%20the%20tremor%20occurred%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20frightening.%20It%20was%20sudden%20and%20abrupt%20and%20I%20was%20worried%20for%20my%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E