C%20the%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20predicted%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20win%2062%20seats%2C%20two%20more%20than%20the%20majority%2C%20and%20the%20BRS%20may%20be%20reduced%20to%2044%20seats.%20The%20BJP-Jana%20Sena%20alliance%20was%20predicted%20to%20win%20seven%20seats%20and%20the%20AIMIM%20five.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20turnout%20in%20the%20November%2030%20election%20was%2071.34%25%2C%20two%20percentage%20points%20less%20than%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnti-incumbency%20has%20been%20building%20up%20against%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20it%20was%20banking%20on%20welfare%20measures%2C%20including%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20and%20Rythu%20Bima%20schemes%20for%20farmers%2C%20Dalit%20and%20BC%20Bandhu%20schemes%20for%20the%20deprived%20classes%20and%20the%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20scheme%20to%20give%20housing%20to%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20and%20the%20IT%20and%20industries%20minister%2C%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%2C%20have%20insisted%20that%20job%20creation%20and%20GDP%20growth%20in%20Telangana%20have%20been%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20many%20sections%20have%20complained%20that%20getting%20employment%20has%20been%20an%20issue.%20The%20implementation%20of%20some%20schemes%20has%20also%20given%20an%20inordinate%20amount%20of%20power%20to%20MLAs%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20distribution%20of%20funds%2C%20leading%20to%20allegations%20of%20discrimination%20as%20well%20as%20corruption.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20perception%20that%20is%20hurting%20the%20party%20is%20that%20KCR%20and%20his%20son%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20run%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20leaves%20little%20room%20for%20dissent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Challengers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESensing%20what%20is%20probably%20the%20first%20real%20opportunity%20to%20form%20a%20government%20in%20the%20state%2C%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20carried%20out%20high-decibel%20campaigns%2C%20with%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20Centre%20organising%20several%20rallies%20not%20just%20by%20its%20talisman%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20but%20also%20several%20Union%20ministers.%20Both%20parties%20have%20also%20tried%20to%20paint%20the%20BRS%20into%20a%20corner%20by%20alleging%20that%20it%20is%20a%20B-team%20of%20the%20other%2C%20a%20charge%20strongly%20denied%20by%20KCR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20claims%20it%20had%20a%20big%20role%20to%20play%20in%20Telangana%20getting%20statehood%20because%20it%20happened%20under%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20revamped%20its%20Telangana%20unit%20in%202021%20and%20appointed%20Revanth%20Reddy%20as%20the%20chief.%20Under%20Mr%20Reddy%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20seen%20to%20have%20mounted%20a%20spirited%20campaign%20and%20he%20has%20also%20indicated%20a%20willingness%20to%20lead%20from%20the%20front%20by%20taking%20on%20KCR%20in%20the%20Kamareddy%20constituency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20also%20addressed%20several%20rallies%20in%20the%20state%20and%20a%20video%20had%20gove%20viral%20when%20he%20had%20interrupted%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20taken%20the%20mic%20and%20shouted%20%26quot%3Bbye-bye%2C%20KCR%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20aspects%20working%20in%20the%20party's%20favour%20is%20the%20six%20guarantees%20it%20has%20given%20to%20the%20voters.%20The%20guarantee%20formula%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20big%20factor%20in%20the%20Congress's%20victory%20in%20neighbouring%20Karnataka%20in%20May%20and%20the%20party%20is%20hoping%20that%20it%20will%20help%20it%20win%20in%20Telangana%20as%20well.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20promised%20that%20the%20six%20guarantees%20would%20be%20approved%20in%20the%20very%20first%20cabinet%20meeting%20if%20the%20party%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guarantees%20include%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month%20for%20eligible%20women%2C%20free%20bus%20travel%20for%20women%2C%20gas%20cylinders%20for%20Rs%20500%2C%20200%20units%20of%20free%20electricity%2C%2024-hour%20power%20to%20farmers%20and%20Rs%204%2C000%20monthly%20pension%20for%20eligible%20senior%20citizens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Campaign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20central%20heavyweights%20have%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20the%20BJP's%20Telangana%20campaign%2C%20the%20removal%20of%20its%20fiery%20state%20chief%2C%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20in%20July%2C%20seem%20to%20have%20hurt%20its%20prospects%2C%20according%20to%20experts%20and%20some%20people%20within%20the%20party.%20It%20was%20after%20Mr%20Kumar's%20removal%2C%20and%20replacement%20with%20Union%20Minister%20G%20Kishan%20Reddy%2C%20that%20the%20perception%20of%20the%20party%20softening%20its%20stance%20against%20the%20BRS%20began%20gaining%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20won%20just%20one%20seat%20in%20the%202018%20Assembly%20polls%20but%2C%20after%20his%20appointment%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20led%20the%20party%20to%20wins%20in%20nearly%20a%20third%20of%20the%20seats%20in%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20in%202020%2C%20an%20outcome%20that%20surprised%20most%20observers.%20He%20also%20contributed%20to%20the%20party's%20victories%20in%20two%20bypolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20acerbic%20speeches%20and%20direct%20attacks%20on%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20energised%20the%20party's%20base%20in%20the%20state%20but%20his%20provocative%20statements%2C%20including%20one%20on%20BRS%20leader%20and%20KCR's%20daughter%20K%20Kavitha%2C%20were%20seen%20as%20reasons%20for%20his%20ouster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECampaigning%20in%20the%20state%2C%20both%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20have%20repeatedly%20attacked%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20quell%20the%20perception%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Bunderstanding%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20BRS.%20The%20party%20has%20said%20it%20will%20appoint%20a%20perso