Congress%20is%20confident%20it%20can%20upset%20its%20rival's%20apple%20cart%2C%20but%20the%20exit%20polls%20disagree%3B%20only%20four%20predict%20a%20return%20close%20to%20the%20116%2B%20seats%20it%20needs%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government%20and%2C%20even%20then%2C%20in%20each%20case%20the%20BJP%20is%20within%20striking%20distance%20in%20a%20state%20they%20have%20dominated%20since%202003.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-exit-polls-live-updates-bjp-and-congress-neck-and-neck-in-madhya-pradesh-predict-exit-polls-4621704%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP%20Likely%20To%20Keep%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3A%20NDTV%20Poll%20Of%20Polls%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20though%2C%20more%20to%20the%20story%2C%20including%20'revenge'%20for%202020%2C%20the%20Kamal%20Nath%20and%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20narratives%2C%20and%20the%20build-up%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Congress%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fkamal-nath%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKamal%20Nath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20this%20is%20a%20chance%20at%20redemption%20after%20the%20events%20of%20March%202020.%20The%20party%20watched%20its%20government%20fall%20and%20was%20left%20in%20disarray%20after%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia's%20revolt%2C%20and%20few%20can%20say%20the%20rebellion%20was%20not%20on%20the%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Fmadhya-pradesh-assembly-election-kamal-nath-kamal-nath-the-man-who-won-madhya-pradesh-for-the-congress-in-2018-4580805%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKamal%20Nath%3A%20The%20Man%20Who%20Won%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20For%20The%20Congress%20In%202018%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20just%20two%20years%20after%20Kamal%20Nath%20orchestrated%20a%20campaign%20that%20won%20the%20Congress%20114%20seats%20-%20two%20short%20of%20an%20outright%20majority%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20a%20big%20result%20in%20a%20state%20the%20BJP%20had%20held%20for%2015%20years.%20In%20each%20of%20the%20three%20previous%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20won%20only%2038%2C%2071%2C%20and%2058%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kamal%20Nath%20quit%20on%20March%2020%2C%202020%2C%20he%20declared%3A%20%26quot%3BThose%20responsible%2C%20remember%20tomorrow%20comes%20after%20today%20and%20day%20after%20comes%20after%20tomorrow.%20The%20day%20after%20will%20come%20for%20sure.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECould%20that%20%26quot%3Bday%20after%26quot%3B%20be%20today%3F%20The%2077-year-old%20held%20over%20100%20rallies%20-%20nearly%20a%20third%20of%20his%20party's%20total%20-%20as%20he%20cross-crossed%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20win%20back%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fshivraj-singh-chouhan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20think%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20doubt.%20It%20is%20said%20there%20is%20a%20close%20contest...%20there%20is%20no%20such%20situation.%20People%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20will%20bless%20the%20BJP%20for%20its%20work%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20four-time%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20walked%20a%20curious%20line%20this%20campaign%20-%20it%20has%20not%20backed%20Mr%20Singh%20for%20a%20fifth%20term%20but%20is%20trying%20to%20capitalise%20on%20his%20'Ladli%20Behna%20Yojana'%20scheme%20for%20women%2C%20which%20it%20hopes%20will%20win%2029%20seats%20-%20of%20which%20the%20Congress%20won%2020%20in%202018%20-%20in%20which%20they%20outnumber%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-news-women-v