74248%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20Has%20Eyes%20On%20Fifth%20Stint%20At%20Top%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20it%20win%2C%20the%20BJP%20might%20have%20little%20choice%20but%20to%20hand%20Mr%20Chouhan%20a%20fifth%20term%2C%20particularly%20since%20he%20is%20also%20an%20OBC%20leader%20in%20a%20state%20that%20has%20a%20massive%20OBC%20population%20-%20over%2050%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fight%20to%20form%20the%20next%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20should%20end%20today%2C%20but%20that%20to%20win%20its%2029%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20is%20just%20getting%20started.%20And%20the%20Congress%20has%20(another)%20mountain%20to%20climb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20may%20not%20have%20as%20many%20Lok%20Sabha%20segments%20as%20other%20states%20-%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Bihar%20all%20have%20more%20-%20but%20its%20seats%20give%20the%20opposition%20a%20chance%20to%20offset%20a%20likely%20headstart%20for%20a%20BJP%20that%20is%20widely%20expected%20to%20sweep%20UP's%2080.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20decimated%20the%20opposition%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20winning%2027%20and%2028%20seats%2C%20respectively%3B%20the%20Congress'%20three%20wins%20across%20two%20elections%20were%20in%20Kamal%20Nath's%20bastion%20of%20Chhindwara%20and%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia's%20Guna.%20Mr%20Scindia%20now%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20with%20the%20BJP.%20The%20(more)%20bad%20news%20for%20the%20Congress%20is%20that%20the%20BJP%20won%20over%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes%20in%20those%20two%20elections%2C%20while%20it%20averaged%20around%2034%20per%20cent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20a%20big%20deficit%20to%20make%20up%2C%20and%20for%20the%20Congress%20the%20first%20steps%20must%20be%20taken%20now%2C%20considering%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20largely%20voted%20for%20the%20same%20party%20in%20each%20of%20the%20last%20two%20state%20and%20general%20elections.%3