%20the%20incumbent%20gets%20voted%20out.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20campaigning%20has%20been%20intense%20on%20both%20sides.%20The%20BJP%20had%20pulled%20all%20stops%20in%20line%20with%20its%20established%20election%20template%2C%20deploying%20senior%20ministers%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20The%20Congress%20had%20followed%20a%20grassroots%20campaign%20with%20frequent%20appearances%20by%20its%20central%20leaders.%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20through%20it%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20projected%20huge%20confidence%2C%20claiming%20he%20has%20beaten%20the%20jinx%20on%20the%20fortunes%20of%20the%20party%20in%20power.%20The%20BJP%20rode%20high%20on%20the%20trend%2C%20and%20the%20power%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20brand.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20as%20the%20polls%20in%20five%20states%20ended%20with%20the%20election%20in%20Telangana%2C%20the%20NDTV%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20--%20an%20aggregate%20of%20nine%20exit%20polls%20---%20indicated%20that%20it%20could%20be%20a%20daunting%20task%20for%20Mr%20Gehlot%20to%20get%20a%20second%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20of%20nine%20exit%20polls%20gave%20the%20BJP%20a%20comfortable%2C%20if%20not%20a%20strong%2C%20victory.%20The%20aggregate%20indicated%20that%20the%20BJP%20may%20get%20104%20seats%20and%20Congress%2086.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%202018%2C%20then%20incumbent%20BJP%20had%20given%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20stopping%20it%20one%20short%20of%20majority.%20There%20is%20a%20chance%20that%20this%20time%2C%20it%20might%20find%20itself%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20fence%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20marked%20difference%20in%20the%20poll%20promises%20of%20the%20two%20parties.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20parties%20have%20made%20provisions%20for%20farmers%2C%20youth%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20women%20and%20various%20groups.%20But%20like%20the%20difference%20in%20the%20price%20of%20cooking%20gas%20they%20are%20offering%20--%20the%20BJP's%20Rs%20450%20to%20Congress's%20Rs%20500%20--%20the%20gap%20is%20marginal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20similarities.%20Over%20the%20better%20part%20of%20five%20years%2C%20both%20parties%20have%20struggled%20to%20contain%20inner%20rifts%20and%20factionalism%20--%20the%20Congress%20more%20publicly%20than%20the%20BJP.%20While%20the%20bickering%20was%20put%20on%20hold%20as%20the%20election%20got%20closer%2C%20the%20united%20front%20--%20especially%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Congress%20--%20could%20take%20a%20backseat%20if%20victory%20is%20achieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ashok%20Gehlot-Sachin%20Pilot%20feud%20over%20the%20top%20job%20has%20made%20headlines%20frequently%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDifferences%20between%20the%20two%20leaders%20surfaced%20shortly%20after%20Mr%20Pilot%2C%20a%20contender%20for%20the%20post%2C%20was%20persuaded%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20be%20Mr%20Gehlot's%20deputy.%20He%20revolted%20in%202020%2C%20bringing%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20to%20the%20brink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20straight%20victory%20for%20the%20Congress%20now%20could%20make%20it%20hard%20for%20the%20Central%20leadership%20to%20deny%20Mr%20Gehlot's%20claims%20for%20a%20fourth%20term.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20Chief%20Ministerial%20candidate%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20key%20factor%20that%20might%20affect%20the%20fortunes%20of%20the%20party%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20crucial%20elections%20that%20are%20seen%20as%20a%20bellwether%20for%20the%202024%20polls%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVasundhara%20Raje%2C%20the%20BJP's%20best-known%20face%20in%20the%20state%2C%20has%20not%20been%20projected%20as%20the%20party's%20Chief%20Ministerial%20candidate%2C%20there%20is%20a%20long%20queue%20for%20the%20top%20job%2C%20with%20state%20BJP%20chief%20CP%20Joshi%2C%20Union%20minister%20Gajendra%20Shekhawat%2C%20Diya%20Ku