0forest%20cover%20%E2%80%93%20are%20an%20ecosystem%20that%20is%20increasingly%20under%20threat%20due%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS1574954122000991%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edegradation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fges.rgo.ru%2Fjour%2Farticle%2Fview%2F2849%2F711%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eencroachment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20developmental%20projects.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F04170315%2F15693039226_bc366e1bf3_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F04170315%2F15693039226_bc366e1bf3_c.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F04170315%2F15693039226_bc366e1bf3_c-300x169.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-568386%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20forest%20in%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Pahalgam.%20Photo%3A%20Flickr%2F%20Ankur%20Panchbudhe%20CC%20BY-SA%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20threats%20to%20the%20environment%20and%20wildlife%20in%20the%20state%20don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20with%20the%20Aravallis%20alone.%20The%20state%20of%20Rajasthan%20is%20one%20of%20the%20last%20strongholds%20of%20the%20great%20Indian%20bustard%2C%20a%20large%20grassland-dwelling%20bird%20that%20very%20narrowly%20missed%20being%20crowned%20the%20national%20bird%20several%20decades%20ago.%20Of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fmagazine%2F2023%2Fmar%2F19%2Fa-fightfor-flight-rajasthansstate-birdgreat-indian-bu