t-in-north-telangana.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eissue%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20state%3A%20as%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalforestwatch.org%2Fdashboards%2Fcountry%2FIND%2F32%2F%3Fcategory%3Dforest-change%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGlobal%20Forest%20Watch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20state%20lost%20135%20hectares%20of%20natural%20forest%2C%20equivalent%20to%20101%20kt%20of%20CO%E2%82%82%20emissions%2C%20in%202022.%20Forest%20fragmentation%20is%20also%20a%20concern%2C%20according%20to%20one%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1007%2Fs10661-015-4673-5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%E2%80%99s%20Chevella%20SC%20ST%20Declaration%20released%20during%20the%20current%20election%20campaign%2C%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20(FRA)%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20strictly%20implemented%20to%20provide%20pattas%20for%20Podu%20lands%20to%20all%20the%20eligible%20beneficiaries.%E2%80%9D%20The%20implementation%20of%20the%20FRA%20has%20been%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20in%20many%20states%2C%20including%20Telangana.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fharitha-haaram-how-telanganas-afforestation-project-proved-detrimental-to-adivasi-rights%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20November%2030%20about%20how%20the%20Haritha%20Haaram%2C%20an%20afforestation%20project%20rolled%20out%20by%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20government%2C%20has%20displaced%20small-scale%20farmers%20and%20tribal%20communities%20in%20its%20wake.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20manifesto%20also%20mentions%20that%20drains%20in%20Hyderabad%20will%20be%20modernized%20to%20make%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cflood-free%E2%80%9D%20city.%20It%20promises%20to%20%E2%80%9Cformulate%20a%20robust%20policy%20for%20flood%2Cdisaster%20management%20and%20heat%20wave%20action%20management%E2%80%9D%20as%20well%20as%20take%20steps%20to%20build%20a%20%E2%80%9Csustainable%20ecosystem%E2%80%9D%2C%20though%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20say%20how%20exactly%20it%20proposes%20to%20do%20so.%20Flooding%20in%20the%20capital%20city%20has%20been%20a%20problem%2C%20with%20around%2095%25%20of%20its%20area%20being%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Frapid-urbanisation-change-in-land-use-resulting-in-frequent-flooding-in-hyderabad%2Farticleshow%2F101265873.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eidentified%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20being%20at%20%E2%80%9Cmoderate%20risk%E2%80%9D%20of%20floods.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERainwater%20pits%20in%20new%20houses%20and%20industrial%20constructions%20will%20be%20made%20compulsory%2C%20and%20people%20will%20be%20identified%20as%20%E2%80%9Cvoluntary%20volunteers%E2%80%9D%20in%20villages%20to%20protect%20the%20trees.%20These%20volunteers%20will%20be%20paid%20an%20honorarium%20to%20protect%20trees%2C%20per%20the%20manifesto.%20The%20Congress%20if%20it%20comes%20into%20power%20will%20implement%20%E2%80%9Call%20measures%20for%20sustained%20environment%20protection%E2%80%9D%20and%20control%20the%20use%20of%20plastic%2C%20and%20encourage%20the%20manufacture%20of%20jute%20and%20coir%20bags.%20Per%20the%20manifesto%2C%20the%20state%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(PCB)%20will%20be%20modernized%20and%20a%20Pollution%20Control%20Ward%20established%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprovide%20better%20services%20in%20the%20prevention%20of%20air%20pollution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20currently%20BJP-ruled%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20several%20environmental%20issues%20abound.%20The%20BJP-ruled%20union%20government%20has%20pushed%20forward%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3EKen-Betwa%20river%20linking%20project%20%3Cspan%3Ein%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20In%20December%202021%2C%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20approved%20the%20Rs.%2044%2C605%20crore%20Ken-Betwa%20river%20interlinking%20project%2C%20apparently%20intended%20to%20address%20water%20scarcity%20of%20the%20Bundelkhand%20region%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20project%20aims%20to%20connect%20the%20Ken%20and%20Betwa%20rivers%20and%20transfer%20water%20from%20the%20former%20to%20the%20latter%20to%20irrigate%20agricultural%20tracts%20of%20and%20supply%20drinking%20water%20to%20the%20water-starved%20Bundelkhand%20region.%20However%2C%20the%20project%20entails%20the%20loss%20of%2023%20lakh%20trees.%20It%20will%20also%20submerge%20around%209%2C000%20hectares%20of%20land%20%E2%80%93%205%2C803%20of%20which%20lie%20within%20the%20core%20area%20of%20the%20Panna%20tiger%20reserve.%20Experts%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Bundelkhand%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20suffer%20for%20decades%20to%20come%E2%80%9D%20if%20this%20project%20is%20implemented.%20Read%20why%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fken-betwa-interlink-means-bundelkhand-will-suffer-for-decades-to-come%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Frti-centre-sc-cec-report-ken-betwa-link-project%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethis%20six-part%20series%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F30134800%2FThe_Royal_Bengal_tiger.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F30134800%2FThe_Royal_Bengal_tiger.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F30134800%2FThe_Royal_Bengal_tiger-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F30134800%2FThe_Royal_Bengal_tiger-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-610872%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Bengal%20tiger.%20Photo%3A%20Pallavibarman10%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProject%20Cheetah%3Cspan%3E%2C%20another%20programme%20implemented%20by%20the%20union%20government%2C%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20programme%20to%20reintroduce%20cheetahs%20(the%20fastest%20land%20mammals%20went%20extinct%20in%20the%20country%20around%20the%201950s)%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-survival-relocation%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eongoing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20MP%E2%80%99s%20Kuno%20National%20Park.%20However%2C%20Project%20Cheetah%20has%20been%20plagued%20by%20several%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetahs-in-kuno-have-neck-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epotentially-avoidable%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20deaths%20of%20African%20cheetahs%20imported%20from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%20by%20the%20government%2C%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsouth-african-scientists-cheetah-project-question%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eissues%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20surrounding%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fkuno-project-cheetah-carrying-capacity%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eability%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20Kuno%20to%20accommodate%20cheetahs%20within%20its%20bounds.%20The%20state%20government%20even%20imposed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fproject-cheetah-media-gag-order%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20gag%20order%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20officials%20to%20not%20talk%20to%20the%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20are%20contesting%20all%20230%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20BSP%20is%20contesting%20218%20seats%2C%20followed%20predominantly%20by%20the%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20(ASP)%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20and%20the%20AAP%2C%20which%20are%20contesting%20between%2066%20to%2086%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMizoram%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMizoram%2C%20currently%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP-allied%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%2C%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20against%20the%20amendment%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3EForest%20Conservation%20Act%3Cspan%3E%20(FCA)%201980%2C%20in%20August%20this%20year.%20The%20new%20amendment%20to%20the%20FCA%2C%20brought%20in%20by%20the%20union%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20will%20remove%20protection%20for%20community%20and%20deemed%20forests%2C%20per%20experts.%20Most%20forestland%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20like%20many%20states%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20comes%20under%20community%20forests.%20The%20FCA%20amendment%20also%20ruled%20that%20projects%20%E2%80%93%20developmental%20or%20those%20pertaining%20to%20national%20security%20%E2%80%93%20within%20a%20100%20km%20radius%20of%20the%20national%20border%20will%20not%20require%20forest%20clearances%2C%20contrary%20to%20what%20the%20FCA%20currently%20imposes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Mizoram%20resolution%20against%20the%20amendment%20emphasized%20the%20%E2%80%9Cneed%20to%20protect%20the%20rights%20and%20interests%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Mizoram%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fmizoram-assembly-adopts-resolution-opposing-forest-conservation-act%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewslick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20state%20environment%20minister%20highlighted%20the%20potential%20threat%20to%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20forest%20cover%20that%20will%20result%20if%20the%20amendment%20is%20brought%20in%20force.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMizoram%E2%80%99s%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20in%20power%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fothers%2Fmnf-will-get-absolute-majority-no-tie-up-with-bjp-mizoram-cm-zoramthanga-101699328485767.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebroke%20off%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20government%20at%20the%20Centre.%20While%20the%20Congress%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Fmizoram-assembly%2Fcongress-will-pass-bill-guaranteeing-protection-of-land-forests-tribal-peoples-rights-in-mizoram-jairam-ramesh%2Farticle67469398.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edeclared%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20it%20will%20pass%20a%20Bill%20guaranteeing%20protection%20of%20land%2C%20forests%2C%20tribal%20people%E2%80%99s%20rights%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20the%20battle%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20tied%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Ftheweek%2Fcurrent%2F2023%2F11%2F04%2Fa-fight-between-zoram-people-s-movement-and-mnf-in-mizoram-elections.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebetween%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20MNF%20and%20the%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20in%20the%20state%2C%20as%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Felections%2Fmizoram-assembly-polls-2023%2Fstory%2Fmizoram-assembly-election-exit-poll-result-2023-live-updates-mizo-national-front-zoram-peoples-party-congress-2469522-2023-11-30%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexit%20polls%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Votes%20will%20be%20%3C%2Fsp