%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20Science%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgovernment%2Fexpanding-oil-palm-plantations-in-the-northeast-could-exact-a-long-term-cost%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20Science%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgovernment%2Foil-palm-plan-should-avoid-catastrophic-mistakes-of-se-asia-scientists-to-pm%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20how%20more%20than%20100%20scientists%20and%20conservationists%20wrote%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20in%20December%202021%2C%20urging%20that%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20newly-launched%20National%20Mission%20on%20Edible%20Oils%20%E2%80%93%20Oil%20Palm%20(NMEO-OP)%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20increase%20the%20extent%20of%20area%20under%20oil%20palm%20cultivation%20in%20India%2C%20incorporate%20a%20scientific%20plan%20for%20the%20expansion%20of%20oil%20palm%20in%20northeast%20India%20and%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20so%20that%20existing%20areas%20are%20tapped%20instead%20of%20biodiversity-rich%20areas%20in%20the%20northeast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOil%20palm%20is%20an%20extremely%20water%20and%20nutrient%20intensive%20crop.%20Per%20a%20detailed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmizoram-shows-why-centres-palm-oil-plans-will-be-disastrous-for-farmers-environment%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Caravan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20both%20farmers%20and%20companies%20have%20found%20that%20it%20is%20a%20failure%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20crop%20due%20to%20this.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701567048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F10143411%2FInto-the-forest-scenery-Gorumara-forest-India-86509-pixahive-1024x631-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fassembly-polls-how-environmental-issues-figured-in-the-electoral-discourse-of-political-parties%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20has%20put%20together%20some%20of%20the%20main%20environmental%20issues%20being%20faced%20by%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Mizoram.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fassembly-polls-how-environmental-issues-figured-in-the-electoral-discourse-of-political-parties%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%20Court%20Grants%20Bail%20to%20Students%20Arrested%20for%20'Chanting%20Pro-Pak%20Slogans'%2C%20Police%20Drop%20Terror%20Charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F28104743%2FF_SqDC5aIAAi4ou.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20court%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20granted%20bail%20to%20the%20seven%20students%20who%20were%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20shouting%20pro-Pakistan%20slogans%20following%20India%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%20the%20cricket%20world%20cup%20final%20last%20month.%20The%20police%20has%20also%20dropped%20its%20terror%20charges%20against%20the%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20in%20central%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Ganderbal%20district%20on%20Saturday%2C%20December%202%2C%20granted%20interim%20bail%20to%20the%20seven%20students%20of%20Sher-e-Kashmir%20University%20of%20Agriculture%20Science%20and%20Technology%20(SKUAST)%2C%20who%20were%20accused%20of%20celebrating%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20victory%20over%20India%20in%20the%20world%20cup%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20complaint%20filed%20by%20a%20SKUAST%20student%20from%20Punjab%20had%20alleged%20that%20pro-Pakistan%20slogans%20were%20shouted%20by%20Kashmiri%20students%20staying%20at%20one%20of%20the%20hostel%20blocks%20in%20the%20university%2C%20while%20non-local%20students%20were%20also%20warned%20against%20rooting%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20complainant%20student%2C%20Sachin%20Bains%2C%20was%20allegedly%20abused%20and%20threatened%20by%20the%20Kashmiri%20students%20who%20shouted%20pro-Pakistan%20slogans%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98Jeeve%20Jeeve%20Pakistan%E2%80%99%20which%20created%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20among%20the%20non-local%20students%20at%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20the%20complaint%2C%20the%20police%20had%20booked%20the%20students%20under%20Section%2013%20(advocating%2C%20abetting%20or%20inciting%20any%20unlawful%20activity)%20of%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%2C%201967%20(UAPA)%20and%20Sections%20505%20(inciting%20communal%20violence)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20terror%20FIR%20had%20prompted%20an%20uproar%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20with%20the%20families%20of%20the%20students%20as%20well%20as%20political%20parties%20and%20common%20netizens%20demanding%20that%20the%20police%20should%20drop%20the%20charges%20and%20give%20the%20students%20a%20second%20chance%20to%20continue%20their%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20while%20terming%20the%20incident%20as%20%E2%80%9Cterrorising%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cabnormal%E2%80%9D%2C%20had%20defended%20the%20anti-terror%20FIR%2C%20saying%20that%20such%20acts%20have%20been%20done%20in%20the%20past%20%E2%80%9Cmostly%20on%20the%20back%20of%20separatist%20and%20terrorist%20networks%E2%80%9D%20to%20project%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceveryone%20hates%20India%E2%80%9D%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20aim%20is%20not%20airing%20personal%20preference%20of%20a%20particular%20sporting%20team.%20It%20is%20not%20about%20dissent%20or%20freedom%20of%20expression.%20It%20is%20about%20terrorising%20others%20who%20may%20be%20nourishing%20pro%20India%20feelings%20or%20anti%20Pakistan%20feelings%20or%20disagreeing%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20November%2028%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20bail%20application%20came%20up%20for%20hearing%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20prosecution%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20police%20prepared%20the%20site%20plan%20of%20scene%20of%20occurrence%20of%20the%20incident%20which%20took%20place%20on%20November%2019%20at%20one%20of%20the%20two%20undergraduate%20hostels%20of%20SKUAST%20in%20the%20Ganderbal%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20investigations%2C%20the%20statements%20of%20witnesses%20were%20recorded%20under%20Section%20161%20of%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20and%20a%20mobile%20phone%2C%20which%20was%20used%20for%20filming%20the%20incident%2C%20was%20also%20taken%20into%20its%20custody%20and%20later%20sent%20to%20FSL%20Srinagar%20for%20analysis%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20the%20prosecution%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20course%20of%20investigation%2C%20CDR%2FSDR%20and%20bank%20details%2Fproperty%20details%20being%20collected%20in%20the%20instant%20case%20and%20the%20correspondence%20has%20been%20taken%20with%20concerned%20units%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prosecution%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20prosecution%20said%20that%20after%20initial%20investigation%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20Section%2013%20of%20the%20anti-terror%20law%20didn%E2%80%99t%20apply%20to%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSenior%20prosecuting%20officer%20analyzed%20circumstances%2C%20evidences%20and%20statements%20on%20record%20opined%20that%20at%20this%20stage%20as%20per%20the%20evidences%20on%20record%20does%20not%20connect%20the%20accused%20persons%20to%20the%20commission%20of%20offences%2013%20UA(P)%20Act%20but%20the%20offence%20under%20section%20153-A%20IPC%20is%20attracted%20in%20the%20instant%20case%20while%20as%20section%2013%20UA(P)%20Act%20is%20dropped%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prosecution%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20the%20statements%20of%20witnesses%2C%20other%20evidences%20and%20legal%20opinion%20so%20far%20section%20153-A%2C%20505%2C%20506%20IPC%20have%20been%20established%20against%20the%20accused%20persons%20in%20the%20instant%20case%20and%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20instant%20case%20is%20going%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prosecution%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20defence%20had%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20students%20were%20%E2%80%9Claw%20abiding%20citizens%E2%80%9D%20who%20%E2%80%9Ccommanded%20the%20respect%20in%20the%20society%20and%20never%20involved%20in%20any%20antisocial%20activities%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20alleging%20that%20they%20were%20being%20%E2%80%9Cimplicated%20in%20a%20false%20and%20frivolous%20case%E2%80%9D%20by%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20the%20two%20sides%2C%20the%20court%20granted%20interim%20bail%20to%20the%20students%20till%20December%2013%20on%20personal%20bonds%20and%20surety%20bonds%20each%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%20among%20other%20conditions.%20The%20court%20asked%20the%20students%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case%20and%20any%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%20activity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20ordered%20the%20students%20to%20remain%20available%20for%20questioning%20regarding%20the%20case.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20investigating%20officer%20shall%20not%20call%20the%20accused%20persons%20after%20sunset%20or%20before%20sunrise%20and%20if%20the%20applicants%20are%20called%20for%20any%20investigation%20purpose%20proper%20record%20shall%20be%20maintained%20in%20the%20CD%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701566830000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fupl