and%20it%20decimated%20the%20BJP%20-%20winning%20174%20and%20172%20of%20230%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20unwelcome%20streak%20could%20end%20today%20with%20victory%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20where%20exit%20polls%20have%20given%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel's%20Congress%20government%20a%20distinct%20edge%20over%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20exit%20polls%20expect%20the%20party%20to%20cross%20the%20majority%20mark%20of%2046%20(the%20Chhattisgarh%20Assembly%20has%2090%20seats)%20on%20its%20own%2C%20two%20more%20predict%2042-44%20and%20the%20remaining%20three%20give%20it%20more%20than%2040%20each.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20two%20of%20nine%20exit%20polls%20give%20the%20BJP%20the%20haul%20of%2046%2B%20seats%20it%20needs%20to%20win%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20score%2C%20when%20the%20dust%20settles%2C%20may%20not%20be%20as%20impressive%20as%20the%2068%20in%202018%20but%2C%20if%20the%20party%20does%20retain%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20major%20boost%20ahead%20of%20next%20year's%20general%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20Mr%20Baghel%20is%20sworn%20in%20for%20a%20second%20term%2C%20it%20will%20be%20despite%20a%20last-minute%20controversy%20-%20corruption%20allegations%20four%20days%20before%20polling%20-%20threatened%20to%20derail%20the%20Congress'%20campaign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20surfaced%20after%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20which%20the%20opposition%20claims%20is%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20target%20rivals%20before%20elections%2C%20arrested%20a%20'hawala'%20courier%20with%20Rs%205%20crore.%20The%20courier%20named%20Mr%20Baghel%20as%20one%20of%20those%20receiving%20kickbacks%20from%20an%20illegal%20online%20gaming%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20week%20after%20the%20second%20and%20final%20phase%20of%20polling%20the%20courier%20retracted%20the%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAway%20from%20the%20corruption%20allegation%2C%20the%20Congress'%20re-election%20campaign%20was%20built%20on%20a%20pro-poor%20and%20pro-farmer%20platform%2C%20including%20Mr%20Baghel's%20price%20support%20guarantee%20for%20rice%2C%20a%20scheme%20to%20purchase%20cow%20dung%20for%20Rs%202%20per%20kg%2C%20and%20the%20promise%20of%20loan%20waivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Baghel%20courted%20OBC%20voters%20-%20they%20account%20for%20over%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20state%20population%20-%20to%20plot%20the%20rebirth%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%202018%2C%20after%20the%202013%20Maoist%20attack%20wiped%20out%20its%20state%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%202023%20election%2C%20the%20canny%20Chief%20Minister%20changed%20tacks%2C%20claiming%20improvements%20in%20infrastructure%20development%20and%20education%2C%20and%20increased%20support%20for%20farmers%2C%20who%20constitue%2C%20by%20some%20estimates%2C%20a%20massive%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20Chhattisgarh's%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20early%20signs%20are%20promising%20for%20the%20Congress%3B%20a%20NDTV%20pre-poll%20survey%20in%20October%20indicated%2039%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20electorate%20would%20be%20happy%20with%20Mr%20Baghel%20to%20continue%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20closest%20BJP%20face%20was%20three-time%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Raman%20Singh%20-%20a%20good%2015%20per%20cent%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2080%20per%20cent%20were%20at%20least%20'somewhat%20satisfied'%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%2C%20on%20governance%2C%20Mr%20Baghel%20scored%20big%20-%2056%20per%20cent%2C%2064%20per%20cent%2C%20and%2053%20per%20cent%20said%20the%20conditions%20of%20roads%2C%20and%20supply%20of%20electricity%20and%20drinking%20water%20had%20improved%20on%20his%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20also%20been%20outmaneuvered%20on%20the%20subject%20of%20religion%20-%20widely%20seen%20as%20its%20go-to%20poll%20platform%20-%20with%20the%20Mr%20Baghel's%20government%20piggybacking%20on%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20this%20be%20enough%20to%20hold%20back%20a%20BJP%20that%20won%20three%20consecutive%20elections%20between%202003%20and%202018%3F%20We'll%20know%20by%20this%20evening%2C%20possibly%20sooner.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701564000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fbfjf1bv8_bhupesh-baghel_625x300_14_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-assembly-election-results-bhupesh-bagel-congress-pass-or-fail-answers-to-congress-bhupesh-baghels-chhattisgarh-exam-today-4627053%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress'%20unwelcome%20streak%20-%20failing%20to%20win%20consecutive%20elections%20in%20a%20state%20-%20could%20end%20today%20with%20victory%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20where%20exit%20polls%20have%20given%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel's%20government%20a%20distinct%20edge%20over%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-assembly-election-results-bhupesh-bagel-congress-pass-or-fail-answers-to-congress-bhupesh-baghels-chhattisgarh-exam-today-4627053%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-assembly-election-results-bhupesh-bagel-congress-pass-or-fail-answers-to-congress-bhupesh-baghels-chhattisgarh-exam-today-4627053%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-assembly-election-results-bhupesh-bagel-congress-pass-or-fail-answers-to-congress-bhupesh-baghels-chhattisgarh-exam-today-4627053%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Battle%20Of%20Nerves%20For%20BJP%2C%20Congress%20-%204%20State%20Election%20Results%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EExit%20polls%20have%20predicted%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20retain%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20reclaim%20Rajasthan.%20The%20Congress%20will%20get%20a%20second%20straight%20term%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20win%20Te