0candidate.%20There%20has%20been%20much%20speculation%20on%20whether%20his%20political%20career%20could%20grind%20to%20a%20standstill.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETelangana%20(119%20seats)%20had%20kept%20faith%20with%20BRS%20--%20which%20played%20a%20key%20part%20in%20the%20statehood%20movement%20%E2%80%93%20since%202014.%20But%20this%20election%20was%20held%20amid%20a%20buzz%20of%20anti-incumbency%20and%20shock%20over%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20claim%20that%20Mr%20Rao%2C%20after%20battling%20for%20a%20non-Congress%20non-BJP%20government%20for%20so%20long%2C%20had%20asked%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%20and%20got%20turned%20down.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20on%20an%20upswing%20after%20its%20huge%20victory%20in%20neighbouring%20Karnataka%2C%20had%20seized%20the%20day%2C%20claiming%20the%20BRS%20was%20hand-in-glove%20with%20the%20BJP.%20As%20icing%2C%20it%20pointed%20out%20that%20unlike%20leaders%20of%20Delhi's%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20Mr%20Rao's%20daughter%20K%20Kavitha%20was%20not%20questioned%20%E2%80%93%20let%20alone%20be%20arrested%20--%20by%20central%20agencies%20even%20though%20her%20name%20cropped%20up%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20scam.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGoing%20by%20the%20exit%20polls%2C%2090-seat%20Chhattisgarh%20could%20be%20the%20only%20state%20where%20the%20Congress%20can%20perhaps%20afford%20to%20relax.%20The%20party%20is%20banking%20on%20the%20track%20record%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20who%20re-built%20the%20party%20in%20the%20state%20after%20the%202013%20Jhiram%20Ghati%20Maoist%20attack.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20both%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20results%20will%20be%20crucial%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Even%20though%20the%20pattern%20of%20state%20and%20general%20elections%20are%20changing%2C%20with%20the%20states%20mostly%20taking%20local%20issues%20into%20account%20for%20assembly%20polls%2C%20a%20victory%20indicates%20a%20solid%20ground%20machinery%20and%20support%20base%20that%20can%20be%20counted%20on%20for%20the%20big%20test.%20A%20Congress%20victory%20in%20Telangana%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20its%20status%20update%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20though%20any%20change%20from%20its%20current%20low%20profile%20can%20affect%20the%20fragile%20balance%20of%20the%20alliance.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701563520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fg25569og_madhya-pradesh-election-2023-gwalior-ani_625x300_02_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-results-2023-battle-of-nerves-for-bjp-congress-4-state-election-results-today-4627396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20counting%20of%20votes%20for%20three%20heartland%20states%20and%20a%20crucial%20one%20in%20the%20south---seen%20as%20a%20bellwether%20ahead%20of%20next%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20--%20begin%20today.%20Mizoram%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20Monday%20after%20objections%20from%20the%20state%20about%20a%20Sunday%20counting%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-results-2023-battle-of-nerves-for-bjp-congress-4-state-election-results-today-4627396%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-results-2023-battle-of-nerves-for-bjp-congress-4-state-election-results-today-4627396%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-results-2023-battle-of-nerves-for-bjp-congress-4-state-election-results-today-4627396%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assembly%20Election%20Results%20Live%3A%20What's%20in%20Store%20for%20Rajasthan%2C%20MP%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Telangana%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02233843%2Fvote-collage.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstro