3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-hostage-mia-schem-operated-gaza-vet-family-says-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22COP28%3A%20India%2C%20China%20Refrain%20From%20Signing%20Plan%20To%20Triple%20Renewable%20Energy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20China%20both%20on%20Saturday%20refrained%20from%20signing%20the%20pledge%20at%20the%20COP28%20climate%20summit%20to%20triple%20the%20world's%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20by%202030%20even%20though%20New%20Delhi%20already%20committed%20to%20it%20as%20part%20of%20its%20G20%20presidency.%20During%20the%20UN's%20climate%20talks%20here%2C%20118%20countries%20committed%20to%20tripling%20the%20global%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20by%202030%20in%20a%20highly%20endorsed%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20ambitious%20goal%20aims%20to%20reduce%20the%20reliance%20on%20fossil%20fuels%20in%20the%20world's%20overall%20energy%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20countries%20which%20backed%20the%20pledge%20included%20Japan%2C%20Australia%2C%20Canada%2C%20Chile%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Nigeria%2C%20and%20Barbados.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20China%20and%20India%20have%20expressed%20endorsement%20for%20the%20threefold%20increase%20in%20renewable%20energy%20by%202030%2C%20neither%20of%20them%20formally%20supported%20the%20comprehensive%20pledge%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20commitment%20involves%20scaling%20up%20clean%20power%20alongside%20a%20decrease%20in%20the%20utilisation%20of%20fossil%20fuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pledge%20called%20for%20phase%20down%20of%20unabated%20coal%20power%20and%20putting%20an%20end%20to%20the%20financing%20of%20new%20coal-fired%20power%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnabated%26quot%3B%20fossil%20fuels%20generally%20refer%20to%20the%20continued%20use%20of%20coal%2C%20oil%20and%20gas%20without%20efforts%20to%20curtail%20emissions.%20Nonetheless%2C%20a%20universally%20accepted%20and%20precise%20definition%20of%20this%20term%20is%20currently%20lacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Energy%20Agency%20says%20the%20world%20must%20triple%20its%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20and%20double%20the%20rate%20of%20energy%20efficiency%20by%202030%20to%20drive%20down%20demand%20for%20fossil%20fuels%20and%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20decision%20has%20gauged%20mixed%20reactions%20from%20Indian%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhura%20Joshi%2C%20Senior%20Associate%20and%20India%20Energy%20Transition%20Lead%20at%20E3G%2C%20expressed%20disappointment%20over%20India's%20decision%20not%20to%20sign%20the%20global%20pledge%20aiming%20to%20triple%20renewable%20energy%20and%20double%20energy%20efficiency%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20pivotal%20decisions%20were%20initially%20championed%20by%20the%20Indian%20G20%20presidency%20and%20endorsed%20by%20G20%20leaders%20in%20September%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20Joshi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoshi%20highlights%20the%20significance%20of%20transitioning%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20particularly%20coal%2C%20to%20achieve%20net-zero%20commitments.%20Despite%20India's%20ambitious%20targets%20for%20renewable%20energy%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20reach%20450GW%20by%202030%2C%20the%20hope%20is%20that%20New%20Delhi%20will%20endorse%20these%20global%20goals%20at%20COP28%2C%20leveraging%20its%20leadership%20position%20in%20the%20renewables%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVibhuti%20Garg%2C%20Director%20of%20South%20Asia%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20Energy%20Economics%20and%20Financial%20Analysis%2C%20notes%20India's%20commitment%20to%20tripling%20the%20renewable%20energy%20target%20as%20part%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20reiterated%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20COP28%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20exhibits%20serious%20ambitions%20for%20renewable%20energy%2C%20Garg%20emphasised%20the%20country's%20silence%20on%20coal%20phase-down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAchieving%20India's%20renewable%20energy%20goals%20will%20necessitate%20a%20tripling%20of%20investments%2C%20prompting%20the%20country%20to%20advocate%20for%20additional%20funding%20support%20from%20the%20Global%20North%20through%20blended%20finance%20mechanisms%2C%20including%20multilateral%20development%20bank%20(MDB)%2C%20green%20bonds%2C%20equity%20investors%2C%20and%20insurance%20and%20pension%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUlka%20Kelkar%2C%20the%20Executive%20Director%20of%20Climate%20at%20World%20Resources%20Institute%20(WRI)%20India%2C%20underscored%20the%20global%20target%20of%20tripling%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20adopted%20during%20India's%20G20%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20highlighted%20the%20magnitude%20of%20India's%20National%20Determined%20Contributions%20(NDC)%20target%2C%20requiring%20the%20country%20to%20build%20as%20much%20renewable%20capacity%20as%20currently%20exists%20on%20the%20entire%20continent%20of%20South%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKelkar%20emphasises%20the%20transformative%20impact%20on%20various%20sectors%2C%20enabling%20vehicles%2C%20buildings%2C%20cookstoves%2C%20and%20industries%20to%20run%20on%20cleaner%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20she%20recognises%20energy%20efficiency%20as%20a%20crucial%20component%20of%20the%20clean%20energy%20transition%2C%20capable%20of%20delivering%20tangible%20benefits%2C%20especially%20for%20micro%2C%20small%2C%20and%20medium%20enterprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ajay%20Mathur%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20the%20International%20Solar%20Alliance%2C%20expresses%20delight%20at%20the%20global%20commitment%20to%20tripling%20renewable%20capacity%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasised%20the%20dual%20benefits%20of%20fostering%20development%20and%20mitigating%20climate%20change%2C%20emphasising%20the%20urgency%20of%20accelerating%20the%20growth%20of%20renewables%20fo