20declared%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20movement%20extremist%2C%20clamping%20down%20on%20gay%20rights%20under%20Putin.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELess%20than%20two%20days%20later%2C%20cops%20raided%20gay%20bars%20and%20clubs%2C%20documenting%20present%20customers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20Russia%20has%20banned%20same-sex%20marriage%20and%20gender%20transition%20care.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20security%20forces%20raided%20gay%20clubs%20and%20bars%20across%20Moscow%20Friday%20night%2C%20less%20than%2048%20hours%20after%20the%20country's%20top%20court%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Frussia-lgbtq-crackdown-extremist-supreme-court-1b8f4cd8708d1c6cf3486c5f27fd7354%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebanned%20what%20it%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20LGBTQ%2B%20movement%26quot%3B%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20an%20extremist%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20searched%20venues%20across%20the%20Russian%20capital%2C%20including%20a%20nightclub%2C%20a%20male%20sauna%2C%20and%20a%20bar%20that%20hosted%20LGBTQ%2B%20parties%2C%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20a%20drug%20raid%2C%20local%20media%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEyewitnesses%20told%20journalists%20that%20clubgoers'%20documents%20were%20checked%20and%20photographed%20by%20the%20security%20services.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20managers%20had%20been%20able%20to%20warn%20patrons%20before%20police%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20raids%20follow%20a%20decision%20by%20Russia's%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20label%20the%20country's%20LGBTQ%2B%20%26quot%3Bmovement%26quot%3B%20as%20an%20extremist%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%2C%20which%20was%20made%20in%20response%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Frussia-lgbtq-crackdown-4f043baf6e1d8999965b815dc5cc7315%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elawsuit%20filed%20by%20the%20Justice%20Ministry%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20latest%20step%20in%20a%20decadelong%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fputin-europe-business-gay-rights-3d08c68ecd95d41511d96336c4f1aa9e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecrackdown%20on%20LGBTQ%2B%20rights%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20who%20has%20emphasized%20%26quot%3Btraditional%20family%20values%26quot%3B%20during%20his%2024%20years%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActivists%20have%20noted%20the%20lawsuit%20was%20lodged%20against%20a%20movement%20that%20is%20not%20an%20official%20entity%2C%20and%20that%20under%20its%20broad%20and%20vague%20definition%20authorities%20could%20crack%20down%20on%20any%20individuals%20or%20groups%20deemed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20LGBTQ%2B%20venues%20have%20already%20closed%20following%20the%20decision%2C%20including%20St.%20Petersburg's%20gay%20club%20Central%20Station.%20It%20wrote%20on%20social%20media%20Friday%20that%20the%20owner%20would%20no%20longer%20allow%20the%20bar%20to%20operate%20with%20the%20law%20in%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMax%20Olenichev%2C%20a%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20who%20works%20with%20the%20Russian%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%2C%20told%20The%20Associated%20Press%20before%20the%20ruling%20that%20it%20effectively%20bans%20organized%20activity%20to%20defend%20the%20rights%20of%20LGBTQ%2B%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20practice%2C%20it%20could%20happen%20that%20the%20Russian%20authorities%2C%20with%20this%20court%20ruling%20in%20hand%2C%20will%20enforce%20(the%20ruling)%20against%20LGBTQ%2B%20initiatives%20that%20work%20in%20Russia%2C%20considering%20them%20a%20part%20of%20this%20civic%20movement%2C%26quot%3B%20Olenichev%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20ruling%2C%20leading%20Russian%20human%20rights%20groups%20had%20filed%20a%20document%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20called%20the%20Justice%20Ministry%20lawsuit%20discriminatory%20and%20a%20violation%20of%20Russia's%20constitution.%20Some%20LGBTQ%2B%20activists%20tried%20to%20become%20a%20party%20in%20the%20case%20but%20were%20rebuffed%20by%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20adopted%20the%20first%20legislation%20restricting%20LGBTQ%2B%20rights%2C%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bgay%20propaganda%26quot%3B%20law%2C%20banning%20any%20public%20endorsement%20of%20%26quot%3Bnontraditional%20sexual%20relations%26quot%3B%20among%20minors.%20In%202020%2C%20constitutional%20reforms%20pushed%20through%20by%20Putin%20to%20extend%20his%20rule%20by%20two%20more%20terms%20also%20included%20a%20provision%20to%20outlaw%20same-sex%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20sending%20troops%20into%20Ukraine%20in%202022%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20ramped%20up%20a%20campaign%20against%20what%20it%20called%20the%20West's%20%26quot%3Bdegrading%26quot%3B%20influence.%20Rights%20advocates%20saw%20it%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20legitimize%20the%20war.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20a%20law%20was%20passed%20banning%20propaganda%20of%20%26quot%3Bnontraditional%20sexual%20relations%26quot%3B%20among%20adults%2C%20also%2C%20effectively%20outlawing%20any%20public%20endorsement%20of%20LGBTQ%2B%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20law%20passed%20this%20year%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Frussia-lgbtq-transgender-procedures-banned-21b88f53b9a74a646400d63ce93bde6f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eprohibited%20gender%20transitioning%20procedures%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20gender-affirming%20care%20for%20transgender%20people.%20The%20legislation%20prohibited%20any%20%26quot%3Bmedical%20interventions%20aimed%20at%20changing%20the%20sex%20of%20a%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20changing%20one's%20gender%20in%20official%20documents%20and%20public%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20authorities%20reject%20accusations%20of%20LGBTQ%2B%20discrimination.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Russian%20media%20quoted%20Deputy%20Justice%20Minister%20Andrei%20Loginov%20as%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20rights%20of%20LGBT%20people%20in%20Russia%20are%20protected%26quot%3B%20legally.%20He%20was%20presenting%20a%20report%20on%20human%20rights%20in%20Russia%20to%20the%20U.N.%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20in%20Geneva%2C%20arguing%20that%20%26quot%3Brestraining%20public%20demonstration%20of%20nontraditional%20sexual%20relationships%20or%20preferences%20is%20not%20a%20form%20of%20censure%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20case%20is%20classified%20and%20it%20remains%20unclear%20how%20LGBTQ%2B%20activists%20and%20symbols%20will%20be%20restricted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20will%20consider%20leaving%20Russia%20before%20they%20become%20targeted%2C%20said%20Olga%20Baranova%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Moscow%20Community%20Center%20for%20LGBTQ%2B%20Initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20clear%20for%20us%20that%20they're%20once%20again%20making%20us%20out%20as%20a%20domestic%20enemy%20to%20shift%20the%20focus%20from%20all%20the%20other%20problems%20that%20are%20in%20abundance%20in%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20Baranova%20told%20the%20AP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flgbtq-rights-russia-moscow-gay-bars-supeme-court-extremist-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701534605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656b597947f9ecb37d896127%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flgbtq-rights-russia-moscow-gay-bars-supeme-court-extremist-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russian%20security%20forces%20raided%20gay%20clubs%20and%20bars%20across%20Moscow%20on%20Friday%2C%20less%20than%2048%20hours%20after%20the%20country's%20top%20court%20banned%20what%20it%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20LGBTQ%2B%20movement.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Associated%20Press)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flgbtq-rights-russia-moscow-gay-bars-supeme-court-extremist-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%20Has%20Emerged%20as%20the%20Keenest%20Contest%20to%20Watch%2C%20Poised%20to%20Throw%20up%20a%20Surprise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18190018%2Fcollage-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Telangana%20was%20the%20last%20of%20the%20five%20states%20to%20go%20to%20polls%20this%20election%20season%2C%20on%20November%2030.%20The%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%20nearly%2010%20years%2C%20faced%20a%20Congress%20on%20fire%2C%20fresh%20from%20a%20victory%20in%20neighbouring%20Karnataka.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20went%20to%20hustings%20with%20its%20earlier%20momentum%20from%20its%20surprising%20excellent%20display%20in%20corporation%20polls%20in%20Hyderabad%20having%20fizzled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20317px)%2085vw%2C%20317px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22317%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22261%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20overwhelming%20number%20of%20pre-poll%20surveys%20and%20exit%20polls%20predict%20a%20sharp%20rise%20in%20those%20preferring%20the%20Congress%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20the%20yawning%20gap%20there%20was%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20Congress%20in%202018%20could%20be%20bridged%2C%20and%20breached.%20Could%20the%20BJP%20spoil%20it%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20by%20eating%20into%20the%20anti-BRS%20vote%3F%20The%20All%20India%20Majlis-E-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20is%20rattled%20but%20is%20expected%20to%20retain%20its%20base%20in%20the%20Old%20City%20of%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20announcing%20its%20candidates%20almost%20three%20months%20back%20in%20August%2C%20the%20BRS%20was%20the%20first%20to%20hit%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20way%20ahead%20of%20others.%20Confident%20of%20winning%20a%20third%20term%2C%20the%20party%20abandoned%20old%20allies%20and%20repeated%20almost%20all%20of%20its%20sitting%20MLAs%2C%20except%20for%20in%20seven%20seats.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20this%20election%20season%20was%20around%20welfare%20schemes%20as%20well%20as%20%E2%80%98successes%E2%80%99%20the%20state%20has%20seen%20in%20the%20power%20and%20irrigation%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20party%20came%20under%20severe%20criticism%20from%20those%20who%20were%20left%20out%20of%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20unemployed%20youth%2C%20and%20disillusioned%20government%20employees.%20It%20was%20also%20criticised%20over%20the%20perceived%20vice-like%20grip%20chief%20minister%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20family%20holds%20on%20the%20levers%20of%20administration%20in%20the%20state%20and%20its%20alleged%20corruption.%20Many%20of%20the%20BRS%20MLAs%20were%20also%20accused%20of%20corruption%20in%20their%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%2C%20which%20is%20now%20in%20reckoning%2C%20was%20completely%20written%20off%20just%20six%20months%20ago.%20Several%20factors%20could%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20upturn%3A%20Perceived%20anti-incumbency%20at%20the%20constituency%20level%20against%20BRS%20MLAs%3B%20energy%20infused%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20victory%20in%20the%20party%20leaders%20and%20cadres%3B%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decline%20following%20the%20removal%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-cracks-appearing-in-bjps-telangana-unit-after-the-karnataka-debacle%5C%22%3EBandi%20Sanjay%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20Telangana%20unit%20chief%3B%20and%20the%20perception%20that%20the%20BRS%20and%20AIMIM%20are%20in%20cahoots%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20fortunes%20over%20the%20last%20six%20months%20have%20diminished%20drastically.%20The%20momentum%20it%20had%20built%20with%20victories%20in%20multiple%20by-polls%20and%20its%20stellar%20performance%20in%20the%20election%20to%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(GHMC)%20had%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20perception%20that%20it%20was%20the%20principal%20challenger%20to%20the%20incumbent%20BRS.%20However%2C%20the%20momentum%20soon%20fizzled%20out.%20Most%20surveys%20indicate%20that%20it%20could%20trail%20as%20a%20distant%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20key%20constituencies%20to%20look%20out%20for%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGajwel%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBRS%20chief%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20has%20held%20this%20seat%20since%202014.%20He%20won%20the%20seat%20comfortably%20both%20in%202014%20and%202018%20assembly%20elections.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20around%20he%20is%20expected%20to%20face%20a%20tough%20fight%20as%20his%20friend-turned-foe%20Eatala%20Rajendar%20has%20thrown%20his%20hat%20in%20the%20ring%20to%20face%20KCR%20in%20a%20direct%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKamareddy%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20constituency%20will%20see%20a%20clash%20between%20KCR%20and%20Congress%20chief%20Revanth%20Reddy.%20Both%20for%20KCR%20and%20Reddy%2C%20Kamareddy%20is%20the%20second%20seat%20that%20they%20are%20contesting.%20The%20presence%20of%20two%20%E2%80%98non-locals%E2%80%99%20said%20to%20be%20working%20in%20favour%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Venkata%20Ramana%20Reddy%2C%20who%20is%20a%20local.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKodangal%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%20chief%20Revanth%20Reddy%20has%20been%20contesting%20from%20this%20seat%20since%202009.%20He%20won%20the%20seat%20in%202009%20and%202014%20assembly%20elections.%20However%2C%20he%20lost%20it%20to%20BRS%20(then%20TRS)%2C%20when%20Reddy%20accused%20BRS%20of%20using%20all%20its%20money%20and%20state%20power%20to%20see%20him%20defeated.%20The%20BRS%20has%20vowed%20to%20defeat%20Reddy%20on%20his%20home%20turf%20once%20again.%20He%20is%20facing%20incumbent%20Patnam%20Mahendar%20Reddy%20of%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESiddipet%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EBRS%20top%20leader%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20has%20been%20winning%20this%20seat%20since%202004%2C%20breaking%20his%20own%20record%20every%20time%20in%20terms%20of%20winning%20majority.%20Rao%20will%20faceoff%20Poojala%20Harikrishna%20of%20the%20Congress%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESiricilla%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBRS%20top%20leader%20and%20IT%20minister%20K.T.%20Rama%20Rao%20will%20face%20off%20K.K.%20Mahendar%20Reddy%20of%20the%20Congress.%20Rao%20has%20held%20the%20seat%20from%202009.%20This%20time%20around%20he%20is%20expected%20to%20face%20a%20tough%20contest%20against%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuzurabad%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Eatala%20Rajendar%20is%20in%20the%20fray%20against%20BRS%20Padi%20Kaushik%20Reddy.%20Rajendar%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20won%20the%20seat%20just%20two%20years%20ago%20in%20a%20bypoll%2C%20necessitated%20by%20his%20%E2%80%98unceremonious%E2%80%99%20exit%20from%20BRS%20and%20his%20resignation%20as%20an%20MLA.%20Despite%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20trounce%20Rajendar%20by%20allegedly%20using%20money%20and%20state%20power%2C%20he%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20the%20bypoll%20in%20November%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarimnagar%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20leader%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20will%20face%20BRS%20minister%