re.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-farmers-votes-at-centre-of-politics-on-paddy-prices-loan-waivers-development%5C%22%3Epaddy%20procurement%3C%2Fa%3E%20prices%20to%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20373px)%2085vw%2C%20373px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22373%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22308%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202018%20elections%2C%20which%20ended%2015%20years%20of%20the%20Raman%20Singh-led%20BJP%20rule%20in%20the%20state%2C%20disenchantment%20among%20paddy%20farmers%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20key%20factors%20along%20with%20anti-incumbency%20that%20helped%20the%20Congress%20dislodge%20the%20saffron%20party%20and%20win%2068%20of%20the%2090%20assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20and%20reduced%20the%20BJP%20to%2015%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20has%20centred%20its%20campaign%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-chhattisgarh-election-raman-singh-bjp-chief-minister-face%5C%22%3Ecorruption%20by%20the%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20learning%20from%20its%20mistake%20in%20the%202018%20defeat%2C%20it%20is%20also%20attempting%20to%20woo%20farmers%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20in%20its%20manifesto%20has%20promised%20to%20procure%20paddy%20at%20Rs%203%2C100%20per%20quintal%20(21%20quintal%20per%20acre)%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%20500%20more%20than%20what%20the%20current%20Congress%20government%20offers.%20It%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20outstanding%20paddy%20procurement%20bonus%20for%20the%20two%20remaining%20years%20of%20the%20Raman%20Singh%20government%20at%20Rs%20300%20per%20quintal%20by%20December%2025%2C%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20called%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-bjps-manifesto-a-copy-of-congress-guarantees-claims-cm-baghel%2F682876.html%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Ccopy%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20its%20promises%20but%20subsequently%20upped%20the%20ante%20and%20promised%20to%20procure%20paddy%20at%20Rs%203%2C200%20(20%20quintal%20per%20acre).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20its%20promises%20to%20farmers%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20also%20pinning%20its%20hopes%20on%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-elections-congress-counts-on-baghel-while-bjp-goes-faceless%5C%22%3Epeople-centric%20schemes%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20NYAY%20(minimum%20wage%20schemes%20for%20farmers%2C%20landless%20labourers%20and%20old-age%20pension)%2C%20Godhan%20Yojana%2C%20Rural%20Industrial%20Parks%20to%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20power.%20It%20has%20also%20invested%20in%20regional%20pride%20through%20the%20Baghel%20government%E2%80%99s%20push%20for%20%E2%80%9CChhattisgarhiyavaad%E2%80%9D%2C%20Ram%20Van%20Gaman%20Path%20and%20building%20various%20temples%20and%20Devgudis%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20snatched%20religion%20as%20an%20issue%20out%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20making%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-has-the-mahadev-app-scam-paradoxically-bolstered-congresss-electoral-prospects%5C%22%3Ecorruption%20by%20the%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20major%20issue%20in%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20also%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-adivasi-christians-struggle-conversion-bogey-narayanpur%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cforced%20conversions%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20tribal%20Adivasi-dominated%20regions%20of%20Bastar%20division%2C%20along%20with%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpm-narendra-modi-congress-naxal-violence-union-government-data%5C%22%3E%20increasing%20Maoist%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20in%20addition%20attempted%20to%20meet%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20challenge%20by%20also%20promising%20pro-people%20assurances%20like%20financial%20assistance%20to%20married%20women%20among%20others%2C%20LPG%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20500%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20also%20attempted%20to%20set%20its%20house%20in%20order%20by%20making%20T.S.%20Singh%20Deo%2C%20who%20has%20been%20at%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-ts-singh-deo-bhupesh-baghel-chhattisgarh%5C%22%3E%20loggerheads%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%20The%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20went%20to%20the%20polls%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-chhattisgarh-election-raman-singh-bjp-chief-minister-face%5C%22%3Ewithout%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20face%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20that%20the%20party%20works%20on%20the%20principle%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccollective%20leadership.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20capitalise%20on%20its%20huge%20success%20in%202018%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20given%20the%20slogan%20of%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAbki%20bar%2075%20paar%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fexit-polls-assembly-elections-2023-november-bjp-congress-brs%5C%22%3Eexit%20poll%20results%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20this%20week%20have%20shown%20a%20neck-and-neck%20fight%20between%20the%20two%20national%20parties%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegions%20%26amp%3B%20Seats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhattisgarh%2C%20with%20a%20tribal%20population%20of%20about%2030%25%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fpolitics%2Fexplainer-chhattisgarh-2023-assembly-election%5C%22%3Ethree%20broad%20regions%20%3C%2Fa%3Eelectorally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20northern%20Adivasi%20belt%20is%20called%20Ambikapur%20or%20Sarguja%20region%20which%20sends%20about%2014%20seats%20to%20the%20assembly.%20This%20includes%20nine%20ST%20seats%2C%20all%20of%20which%20were%20swept%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%202018%2C%20largely%20believed%20to%20be%20under%20the%20influence%20and%20leadership%20of%20Singh%20Deo.%20Singh%20Deo%2C%20who%20is%20fighting%20from%20the%20Ambikapur%20constituency%20again%20is%20a%20three-term%20MLA%20from%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20region%20with%20its%20large%20cities%2C%20major%20OBC%20populations%20and%20agrarian%20areas%20which%20accounts%20for%20about%2064%20constituencies.%20While%20the%20Congress%20swept%20the%20region%20in%202018%2C%20both%20parties%20have%20registered%20victories%20here%20in%20previous%20elections%20with%20variations%20only%20in%20a%20few%20seats.%20The%20Congress%20had%20a%20small%20lead%20in%202008%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20southern%20Bastar%20region%20is%20also%20Adivasi-dominated.%20Bastar%20is%20also%20known%20for%20widespread%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-maoist-dantewada-development%5C%22%3EMaoist%20activities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdivasi-dominated%20Bastar%20with%2012%20seats%20in%20southern%20Chhattisgarh%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanti-bjp-anti-congress-where-the-tussle-lies-in-bastar%5C%22%3Ecrucial%20region%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state%2C%20with%20the%20common%20refrain%20that%20whichever%20party%20wins%20Bastar%2C%20wins%20the%20state.%20An%20exception%20in%20the%20trend%20was%20in%202013%20when%20the%20Congress%20won%20the%20majority%20in%20the%20region%20but%20lost%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20union%20minister%20and%20Sarva%20Adivasi%20Samaj%20(umbrella%20organisation%20of%20tribal%20groups%20in%20the%20state)%20chief%20Arvind%20Netam%E2%80%99s%20new%20political%20outfit%20the%20Hamar%20Raj%20Party%20is%20also%20in%20the%20fray%20and%20has%20declared%20to%20be%20fighting%20for%20PESA%20rights%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchhattisgarh-adivasis-bjp-congress-arvind-netam%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Cjal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20of%20the%20key%20constituencies%20to%20look%20out%20for%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Incumbent%20chief%20minister%20Baghel%20is%20facing%20off%20against%20his%20nephew%20and%20BJP%20MP%20Vijay%20Baghel.%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20has%20won%20five%20times%20from%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERajnandgaon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20chief%20minister%20Raman%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20home%20turf%20and%20has%20won%20the%20last%20two%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20from%20the%20seat.%20The%20BJP%20strongman%20who%20ruled%20Chhattisgarh%20for%2015%20years%20(2003-08)%20is%20facing%20off%20against%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20Girish%20Dewangan%2C%20a%20key%20OBC%20leader%20and%20close%20aide%20of%20CM%20Baghel%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbikapur%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDeputy%20chief%20minister%20Singh%20Deo%E2%80%99s%20constituency%2C%20who%20has%20won%20the%20last%20three%20elections%20from%20the%20seat.%20He%20is%20facing%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rajesh%20Agrawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKonta%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Long%20term%20Congress%20MLA%20Kawasi%20Lakhma%20who%20is%20also%20industry%20and%20excise%20minister%20in%20the%20Baghel%20government%20and%20is%20facing%20opposition%20from%20his%20constituency%20over%20his%20handling%20of%20protests%20in%20the%20region%2C%20including%20Silger%20which%20last%20over%20a%20year.%20CPI%E2%80%99s%20Manish%20Kunjam%2C%20a%20popular%20face%20in%20the%20region%20is%20also%20contest%20from%20Konta%20but%20is%20facing%20a%20setback%20in%20the%20form%20of%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20election%20symbol%20which%20has%20been%20changed%20from%20hammer%20and%20sickle%20to%20air%20conditioner.%20The%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20Salwa%20Judum%20(a%20people%E2%80%99s%20militia%20movement%20against%20Maoists%20started%20by%20late%20Congress%20leader%20Mahendra%20Karma)%20face%2C%20Soyam%20Muka%2C%20who%20has%20a%20good%20rapport%20with%20tribal%20sub-groups%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKondagaon%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECongress%20MLA%20Mohan%20Markam%2C%20the%20ex-Pradesh%20Congress%20chief%2C%20and%20BJP%20national%20vice%20president%20Lata%20Usendi%20are%20facing%20off%20in%20a%20fight%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurg%20Rural%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%20minister%20Tamradhwaj%20Sahu%20who%20helped%20consolidate%20the%20OBC%20votes%20along%20with%20Baghel%20in%202018%20elections%20is%20facing%20off%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Lalit%20Chandrakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaipur%20city%20south%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMahant%20Ramsundar%20Das%20of%20the%20Dudhadhari%20Temple%20is%20facing%20off%20against%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Brijmohan%20Agrawal%20who%20has%20won%20the%20seat%20for%20seven%20consecutive%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDantewada%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELate%20Congress%20MLA%20Mahendra%20Karma%20who%20started%20Salwa%20Judum%20(people%E2%80%99s%20militia%20against%20Maoists)%E2%80%99s%20son%20Chhavindra%20Karma%20is%20fighting%20on%20the%20seat%20where%20his%20mother%20Devati%20Karma%20is%20the%20sitting%20MLA.%20He%20is%20facing%20off%20against%20Chaitram%20Atami%20another%20Judum%20leader%2C%20in%20a%20fight%20that%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBellwether%20seats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20bellwether%20seats%20that%20always%20vote%20the%20way%20the%20state%20votes%20include%20Jashpur%2C%20Nawagarh%2C%20Dongargarh%2C%20Jagdalpur%20and%20Bijapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701528278000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F19162810%2FF_H0xndXcAAdd-S.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwill-paddy-be-the-clincher-in-chhattisgarh-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20is%20looking%20to%20dislodge%20the%20Bhupesh%20Baghel-led%20Congress%20government%2C%20which%20is%20looking%20to%20return%20to%20power%20by%20pinning%20its%20hopes%20on%20its%20winning%20formula%20of%20farm%20loan%20waivers%20and%20increased%20paddy%20procurement%20prices%20to%20farmers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwill-paddy-be-the-clincher-in-chhattisgarh-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22COP28%3A%20UN%20climate%20talks%20go%20big%20on%20ending%20fossil%20fuels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701527124000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F13C36%2Fproduction%2F_131905908_gettyimages-1427900101.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67599925%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Countries%20and%20companies%20pledge%20more%20renewables%20and%20emissions%20cuts%20but%20critics%20say%20the%20measures%20fall%20short.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A137%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67599925%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww