%20Parliament%20Session%20Likely%20as%20Ethics%20Panel%20to%20Table%20Report%20on%20Mahua%20Moitra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F04145325%2F2022_2img03_Feb_2022_PTI02_03_2022_000159B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Called%20just%20a%20day%20after%20the%20results%20of%20the%20much-awaited%20state%20assembly%20polls%20are%20out%2C%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20parliament%20is%20set%20to%20be%20one%20where%20passions%20run%20high.%20Add%20to%20it%20the%20fact%20that%20opposition%20parties%20are%20determined%20to%20oppose%20the%20report%20by%20the%20Ethics%20committee%20recommending%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Mahua%20Moitra%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20her%20Lok%20Sabha%20term.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20list%20of%20business%20released%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretariat%20stated%20that%20either%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20chairman%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Sonkar%20or%20committee%20member%20Aparajita%20Sarangi%20would%20table%20the%20report%20in%20the%20lower%20house%20on%20December%204%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20winter%20session.%20Recently%2C%20the%20committee%20recommended%20expulsion%20of%20Moitra%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20following%C2%A0%20a%20contested%20probe%20on%20allegations%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccash%20for%20query%E2%80%9D%20against%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20even%20the%20most-bitter%20critic%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20has%20said%20that%20expulsion%20of%20TMC%20MP%20Moitra%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ean%20extremely%20serious%20punishment%20and%20has%20very%20wide%20ramifications%E2%80%9D.%20Shooting%20off%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%2C%20Chowdhury%20said%20that%20the%20report%20has%20recommended%20expulsion%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20inadequate%20evidence%2C%20and%20without%20any%20clear%20cut%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%9Cunethical%20conduct%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20records%2C%20prior%20to%20Ms%20Mohua%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20dealt%20with%20a%20minuscule%20number%20of%20cases%20which%20mainly%20pertained%20to%20purported%20acts%20of%20deviation%20from%20the%20general%20norms%20of%20conduct%20and%20the%20punitive%20action%20recommended%20being%20confined%20to%20admonition%2C%20reprimand%20and%20suspension%20from%20the%20Sittings%20of%20the%20House%20for%20a%20specified%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20MP%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20media%20reports%20on%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20on%20choosing%20to%20recommend%20expelling%20Ms%20Mohua%20Moitra%20from%20Parliament%20are%20right%2C%20it%20would%2C%20perhaps%20be%20the%20first%20such%20recommendation%20of%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20of%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Expulsion%20from%20Parliament%2C%20you%20will%20agree%20Sir%2C%20is%20an%20extremely%20serious%20punishment%20and%20has%20very%20wide%20ramifications%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fexpulsion-of-tmc-mp-extremely-serious-punishment-adhir-writes-to-ls-speaker-101701502588149.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChowdhury%20said%20in%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20other%20MPs%20have%20also%20said%20that%20they%20would%20oppose%20any%20attempt%20by%20the%20government%20to%20expel%20Moitra.%20However%2C%20the%20rules%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20say%20that%20if%20a%20motion%20to%20approve%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20ethics%20committee%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fls-ethics-committee-mahua-moitra-expulsion-9020642%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20adopted%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20with%20a%20majority%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Moitra%20will%20stand%20expelled%20the%20very%20moment.%20Going%20by%20the%20brute%20majority%20the%20government%20enjoys%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20expulsion%20looks%20imminent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20had%20alleged%20that%20Moitra%20sought%20favours%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20against%20industrialist%20Gautam%20Adani.%20Later%2C%20Hiranandani%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20also%20backed%20the%20claims.%20However%2C%20Moitra%20denied%20all%20allegations%20and%20challenged%20the%20committee%20to%20find%20concrete%20evidence%20against%20any%20wrongdoing%20by%20her.%20The%20probe%20itself%20saw%20opposition%20members%20boycotting%20what%20they%20called%20a%20leading%20probe%20to%20punish%20Moitra%2C%20but%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20the%20committee%20from%20recommending%20her%20expulsion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20the%20committee%20sent%20the%20report%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20speaker%20Om%20Birla%2C%20who%20has%20now%20decided%20that%20the%20report%20will%20be%20tabled%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20winter%20session.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20MP%20Adhir%20Chowdhury%2C%20in%20his%20letter%2C%20has%20also%20asked%20why%20was%20Hiranandani%2C%20on%20whose%20claim%20that%20he%20had%20access%20to%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20log-in%20credentials%20the%20ethics%20committee%20recommended%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20expulsion%2C%20not%20called%20for%20deposing.%20He%20implied%20that%20it%20may%20be%20possible%20that%20the%20businessman%20may%20be%20under%20some%20pressure%2C%20and%20said%20that%20the%20reasons%20for%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20businessman%20friend%20turning%20against%20her%20is%20not%20known%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAccepting%20gifts%20and%20giving%20gifts%2C%20which%20may%20appear%20to%20be%20expensive%20depending%20on%20the%20yardstick%20applied%2C%20is%20a%20common%20social%20practice%2C%20and%20it%20would%20be%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20link%20or%20attribute%20accepting%20gifts%20to%20be%20a%20money%20trail%20for%20deriving%20favours%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chowdhury%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20case%20had%20no%20similarity%20with%20the%20serious%20%E2%80%9Ccash-for-query%E2%80%9D%20scam%20in%202005%20in%20which%2011%20MPs%20were%20expelled%20from%20the%20House.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20concerned%20in%20the%202005%20case%2C%20including%20the%20media%20personnel%2C%20who%20carried%20out%20the%20Sting%20operation%2C%20and%20members%20accused%20of%20having%20indulged%20in%20acts%20of%20a%20misdemeanour%20were%20examined%20on%20oath%2C%20their%20evidence%20recorded%20and%20made%20part%20of%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Panel.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20whether%20the%20well-established%20procedure%20was%20followed%20and%20a%20money%20trail%20that%20is%20irrefutable%20has%20been%20established%20in%20case%20of%20the%20complaint%20or%20allegation%20against%20Ms%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chowdhury%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20the%20rules%20require%20the%20ethics%20committee%20to%20conduct%20a%20fully%20confidential%20probe%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20as%20well%20as%20the%20complainant%20member%20were%20openly%20parading%20their%20views%20and%20passing%20judgments%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cadvancements%20in%2C%20and%20adoption%20of%20digital%20technologies%20has%20brought%20about%20a%20sea%20change%20in%20the%20processes%20followed%20in%20conducting%20Parliaments%20Business%2C%20including%20the%20Question%20Hour%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20Members%20may%20become%20susceptible%2C%20and%20unwittingly%20find%20themselves%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwrong%20side%E2%80%9D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20sure%20that%20under%20your%20leadership%20and%20control%2C%20no%20injustice%20will%20be%20done%2C%20and%20the%20processes%20relating%20to%20the%20functioning%20of%20Parliament%20and%20conduct%20of%20the%20Business%20of%20the%20House%20is%20smoothened%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20all%20Members%20of%20the%20House%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETMC%20MPs%20planned%20to%20have%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20while%20they%20also%20demanded%20that%20a%20discussion%20should%20be%20held%20in%20the%20Parliament%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20leaking%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20on%20Moitra%20to%20the%20media.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701526462000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F04145325%2F2022_2img03_Feb_2022_PTI02_03_2022_000159B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fstormy-start-to-parliament-session-likely-as-ethics-panel-to-table-report-on-mahua-moitra%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20MPs%2C%20including%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20of%20Congress%20rally%20behind%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20question%20if%20ethics%20committee%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20expel%20someone%20elected%20by%20the%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fstormy-start-to-parliament-session-likely-as-ethics-panel-to-table-report-on-mahua-moitra%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aamir's%20take%20on%20violence%2C%20sex%20in%20movies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701526169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105682612%2Cimgsize-36162.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.