ademics%20accused%20the%20regulator%20of%20drafting%20academic%20institutions%20into%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccult-building%E2%80%9D%20exercise%20they%20should%20%E2%80%9Chave%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Funiversity-grants-commission-asks-universities-colleges-to-set-up-selfie-points-with-images-of-narendra-modi-in-the-background%2Fcid%2F1983967%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20unique%20opportunity%20to%20harness%20the%20energy%20and%20enthusiasm%20of%20the%20youth%2C%20moulding%20their%20minds%20with%20inspiration%20drawn%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20progress%20in%20diverse%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Funiversity-grants-commission-asks-universities-colleges-to-set-up-selfie-points-with-images-of-narendra-modi-in-the-background%2Fcid%2F1983967%5C%22%3Esays%20a%20letter%20from%20UGC%20secretary%20Manish%20Joshi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sent%20to%20the%20vice-chancellors%20of%20all%20Indian%20universities%20and%20the%20principals%20of%20all%20the%20colleges%20on%20Friday%20(December%201).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fugc-directs-maharashtra-universities-to-celebrate-rss-abvp-leaders-birth-centenary%5C%22%3EUGC%20Directs%20Maharashtra%20Universities%20To%20Celebrate%20RSS-ABVP%20Leader%E2%80%99s%20Birth%20Centenary%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20celebrate%20and%20disseminate%20the%20incredible%20strides%20made%20by%20our%20country%20by%20establishing%20a%20%E2%80%98Selfie%20Point%E2%80%99%20within%20your%20institution.%20The%20aim%20of%20%E2%80%98Selfie%20Point%E2%80%99%20is%20to%20create%20awareness%20among%20the%20youth%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20various%20fields%2C%20particularly%20the%20new%20initiatives%20under%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%202020%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fnational-education-national-education-policy-right-to-education%5C%22%3ENEP%202020%20was%20widely%20criticised%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20universities%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fover-150-students-teachers-join-50-day-nationwide-campaign-against-nep-call-for-rollback%5C%22%3Estudents%20and%20teachers%20holding%20several%20protests%20against%20its%20implementation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20UGC%E2%80%99s%20directive%2C%20each%20selfie%20point%20should%20be%20established%20at%20a%20strategic%20place%20on%20the%20campus%20and%20have%20a%203D%20layout.%20It%20has%20also%20recommended%20various%20themes%20like%20internationalisation%20of%20education%2C%20unity%20in%20diversity%2C%20Smart%20India%20Hackathon%2C%20Indian%20knowledge%20system%2C%20multilingualism%2C%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20rise%20in%20higher%20education%2C%20research%20and%20innovation%20for%20the%20photo-ops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20faculty%20member%20at%20a%20top%20institution%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20saying%20that%20the%20government%20was%20portraying%20every%20ordinary%20achievement%20as%20a%20spectacular%20one%20and%20attributing%20the%20credit%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fnational-education-national-education-policy-right-to-education%5C%22%3EThe%20NEP%20Goes%20Against%20the%20Existing%20Constitutional%20Mandate%20of%20the%20RTE%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20happening%20is%20full-blown%20propaganda%20to%20build%20a%20cult%20figure.%20The%20State%20is%20doing%20it%20using%20public%20institutions%20that%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20these%20activities.%20There%20is%20no%20provision%20in%20the%20law%20to%20enable%20the%20government%20or%20the%20UGC%20to%20ask%20academic%20institutions%20to%20promote%20such%20propaganda%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20subtle%20perception%20is%20being%20created%20that%20only%20one%20leader%20is%20responsible%20for%20all%20these%20activities.%20This%20is%20being%20done%20to%20misguide%20gullible%20voters%20keeping%20the%20elections%20in%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20academic%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20management%20teacher%20told%20that%20paper%20the%20UGC%20keeps%20issuing%20such%20circulars%20but%20the%20campus%20administrations%20is%20free%20to%20ignore%20them.%20%E2%80%9C(Educational)%20institutions%20should%20not%20heed%20such%20advice.%20Those%20institutional%20leaders%20who%20are%20not%20sycophants%20will%20be%20able%20to%20ignore%20this%20kind%20of%20advice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701504604000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29095001%2FScreenshot-2023-11-29-at-9.49.41-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fugc-urges-universities-to-set-up-narendra-modi-selfie-points-on-campuses-to-foster-pride%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20UGC%E2%80%99s%20directive%2C%20each%20selfie%20point%20should%20be%20established%20at%20a%20strategic%20place%20on%20the%20campus%20and%20have%20a%203D%20layout.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A77%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fugc-urges-universities-to-set-up-narendra-modi-selfie-points-on-campuses-to-foster-pride%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tea%20production%20rises%2012.06%25%20to%20182.84%20million%20kg%20in%20October%3A%20Industry%20body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701503763000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2017-04%2F07%2Ffull%2F1491503514-5771.jpg%22%2C%22ori