e%20are%20allegations%20that%20the%20paper%20has%20been%20recalled%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20Besides%20the%20one%20cited%20above%2C%20two%20other%20papers%20have%20been%20withdrawn%20pending%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinternal%20review%E2%80%9D%20as%20well%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20and%20procedural%20issues%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20same%20breath%2C%20the%20World%20Bank%20also%20notes%20that%20the%20papers%20published%20on%20its%20website%20go%20through%20required%20approvals%20internally%20before%20they%20are%20made%20available%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contentious%20paper%20%E2%80%93%20Progress%20on%20Sanitation%20in%20Rural%20India%3A%20Reconciling%20Diverse%20Evidence%20%E2%80%93%20published%20in%20September%20concluded%20that%20despite%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fdespite-early-gains-of-swachh-bharat-mission-toilet-use-declining-since-2018-19-world-bank-paper%2Farticle67376731.ece%5C%22%3Ebreathtaking%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20gains%20in%20increasing%20toilet%20access%2C%20toilet%20usage%20had%20been%20going%20down%20in%20rural%20India%20since%202018.%20The%20largest%20drop%20in%20usage%20is%20reported%20among%20people%20from%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(20%20percentage%20points)%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(24%20percentage%20points)%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20findings%20fly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20that%20practices%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fdespite-early-gains-of-swachh-bharat-mission-toilet-use-declining-since-2018-19-world-bank-paper%2Farticle67376731.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Eopen%20defecation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20manual%20scavenging%20no%20longer%20exist%20in%20India%2C%20based%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20toilet%20access%20had%20improved%20after%20the%20building%20of%20over%20100%20million%20toilets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20government%20spokesperson%2C%20whom%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpurely%20World%20Bank%20issue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20under%20scanner%20was%20churned%20out%20based%20on%20the%20data%20points%20on%20toilet%20access%20and%20usage%20from%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20National%20Family%20Health%20Surveys%2C%20National%20Sample%20Surveys%2C%20the%20National%20Annual%20Rural%20Sanitation%20Survey%20(NARSS)%2C%20and%20the%20Swachch%20Bharat%20Mission-Grameen%E2%80%99s%20information%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NARSS%2C%20conducted%20across%20rural%20India%20from%202017-18%20to%202019-20%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Drinking%20Water%20and%20Sanitation%20with%20World%20Bank%20support%2C%20showed%20that%20as%20the%20SBM-G%20began%2C%20it%20led%20to%20a%20substantial%20increase%20in%20access%20to%20own%20or%20shared%20improved%20toilets%20in%20rural%20India.%20It%20rose%20from%2038%25%20in%202012%20to%2090%25%20in%202019-20%2C%20and%20the%20last%20two%20years%20during%20this%20period%20saw%20the%20fastest%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20national%20level%2C%20regular%20use%20of%20any%20toilet%20%5Bimproved%20or%20unimproved%5D%20increased%20from%2046%25%20to%2075%25%20on%20average%20in%20rural%20areas%20during%202015-16%20and%202019-21.%20This%20increase%20was%20across%20all%20population%20and%20socio-economic%20sub-groups%20we%20track%2C%20and%20especially%20pronounced%20for%20the%20poor%20and%20socially%20disadvantaged%20groups%2C%E2%80%9D%20concluded%20the%20now-withdrawn%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20had%20been%20reversals.%20Even%20as%20the%20regular%20use%20of%20any%20toilet%20for%20SC%20(51%20percentage%20points)%20and%20ST%20(58%20percentage%20points)%20people%20saw%20a%20jump%20between%202015-16%20and%202018-19%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20the%20same%20level%20as%20those%20in%20the%20General%20Category%2C%20the%20paper%20said%20these%20gains%20had%20begun%20to%20reverse%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20from%202018%2C%20there%20had%20been%20a%2020%20percentage%20point%20decline%20in%20regular%20use%20of%20toilets%20for%20the%20SC%20population%20and%20a%2024%20percentage%20point%20decline%20for%20the%20ST%20population%20in%20comparison%20to%20a%20decline%20of%209%20and%205%20percentage%20points%20for%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Caste%20and%20General%20categories%20respectively%2C%20the%20paper%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701502892000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fopen-defecation-swachh-barat_flickr.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fworld-banks-research-paper-that-concluded-declining-trend-of-toilet-usage-in-india-withdrawn%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20allegations%20that%20the%20paper%20has%20been%20recalled%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20Modi%20government.%20The%20findings%20of%20the%20paper%20fly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20government's%20claims%20that%20practices%20such%20as%20open%20defecation%20and%20manual%20scavenging%20no%20longer%20exist%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fworld-banks-research-paper-that-concluded-declining-trend-of-toilet-usage-in-india-withdrawn%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Optics%20Aside%2C%20the%20Truth%20Behind%20Manipur's%20Ceasefire%20Agreement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02120041%2FGAQUezCWwAAHb9J.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20famed%20Kangla%20Fort%20standing%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20capital%20Imphal%20is%20today%20witness%20to%20an%20event%20that%20has%20all%20the%20makings%20of%20an%20acrimonious%20chapter%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20state%E2%80%99s%20insurgent%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%E2%80%99s%20special%20event%2C%20commencing%20at%20the%20citadel%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20majority%20community%2C%20the%20Meiteis%2C%20at%2011%20am%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20chief%20minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20will%20clearly%20have%20two%20beneficiaries%20%E2%80%93%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20other%20figures%20in%20the%20limelight%2C%20militant%20leaders%20Kh.%20Pambei%20and%20Th.%20Thanil%2C%20can%20at%20best%20be%20put%20for%20now%20as%20the%20ones%20who%20caved%20in%20to%20the%20pressures%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20and%20the%20Biren%20government%20to%20experiment%20with%20a%20peace%20that%20may%20descend%20on%20the%20valley%20areas%20of%20Manipur%20someday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20central%20and%20the%20state%20governments%20are%20concerned%2C%20the%20Kangla%20event%20will%20certainly%20help%20swell%20their%20optics%2C%20spread%20nationwide%20three%20days%20ago%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20by%20announcing%20that%20his%20ministry%20had%20signed%20a%20ceasefire%20agreement%20with%20%E2%80%98Manipur%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20valley-based%20armed%20group%2C%20the%20United%20Nationalist%20Liberation%20Front%20(UNLF)%E2%80%99%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeace%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20across%20the%20North-East%20long-mired%20in%20conflict%2C%20particularly%20so%20in%20Manipur%20which%20is%20simmering%20in%20ethnic%20strife%20even%20after%20six%20months%20have%20passed.%20However%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20latest%20declaration%20of%20%E2%80%98peace%E2%80%99%20by%20both%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Imphal%20in%20the%20valley%20areas%20is%20a%20bit%20opaque.%C2%A0%20What%20meets%20the%20eye%20is%20more%20optics%20than%20the%20truth%20on%20the%20ground.%20A%20bit%20of%20explaining%20is%20warranted%20then%3B%20the%20mist%20around%20the%20optics%20led%20by%20Shah%20himself%20needs%20lifting%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20facts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Frk-meghan-rebel-leader-manipur-arrives-imphal%5C%22%3EManipur%E2%80%99s%20Rebel%20Leader%20R.K.%20Meghan%20Arrives%20in%20Imphal%20After%20a%20Gap%20of%2044%20Years%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIs%20it%20the%20UNLF%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20called%20the%20group%20that%20has%20agreed%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20the%20government%20as%20%E2%80%98UNLF%E2%80%99.%20What%20he%20kept%20away%20from%20his%20statement%20was%20the%20whole%20truth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reality%20is%20that%20it%20is%20only%20a%20faction%20of%20the%20UNLF%20%E2%80%93%20much%20smaller%20in%20terms%20of%20cadre%20capacity%20than%20the%20one%20that%20has%20decided%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20latest%20%E2%80%98ceasefire%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kh.%20Pambei%20group%2C%20seen%20close%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20state%2C%20has%20only%2065%20cadres%20while%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20K.H.%20Achou%20Singh%2C%20better%20known%20as%20Koireng%2C%20holds%20control%20over%20300%20cadres.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUNLF%20has%20led%20the%20oldest%20insurgency%20in%20the%20North-East%20after%20the%20Naga%20Insurgency.%20That%20it%20may%20want%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20the%20Union%20is%20a%20welcome%20move.%20However%2C%20it%20must%20also%20be%20kept%20in%20mind%20that%20a%20large%20section%20of%20UNLF%20is%20not%20yet%20ready%20for%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20Modi%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02120815%2FGAG0b4EaAAAF2cT.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22934%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02120815%2FGAG0b4EaAAAF2cT.jpeg%20934w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02120815%2FGAG0b4EaAAAF2cT-300x200.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687362%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22623%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20with%20a%20faction%20of%20the%20UNLF.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40NBirenSingh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20non-talks%20faction%20are%20holding%20on%20to%20their%20demand%20that%20for%20talks%20to%20roll%2C%20dialogue%20on%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98sovereignty%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98plebiscite%E2%80%99%20must%20be%20on%20the%20table%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98third%20party%20as%20witness%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPambei%20and%20his%20general%20secretary%20Th.Thanil%20may%20form%20part%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20celebratory%20function%20at%20Kangla%20but%20the%20gulf%20within%20the%20overall%20UNLF%20leadership%20has%20certainly%20made%20put%20them%20in%20an%20uneasy%20spot.%20That%20uneasiness%20was%20palpable%20in%20the%2059%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Raising%20Day%20of%20UNLF%20held%20on%20November%2024%20in%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThanil%2C%20speaking%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20reiterated%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community%20that%20the%20armed%20group%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20surrendering%E2%80%9D%20to%20India%20but%20is%20party%20to%20a%20process%20that%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98political%20settlement%E2%80%99%20of%20their%20struggle.%20He%20referred%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfeelers%E2%80%9D%20from%20New%20Delhi%20prodding%20them%20to%20ponder%20over%20it.%20Pambei%20was%20missing%20from%20the%20event.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConcurrently%2C%20the%20non-talks%20faction%20of%20UNLF%2C%20celebrating%20its%20Raising%20Day%2C%20accused%20the%20Pambei%20faction%20of%20not%20only%20%E2%80%9Cundermining%E2%80%9D%20their%20%E2%80%9Cprincipled%20stand%E2%80%9D%20but%20also%20%E2%80%9Cmisleading%20the%20people%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUltimately%2C%20our%20sovereignty%20and%20independence%20will%20be%20compelled%20to%20sell%20out%20as%20the%20price%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98development%20package%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%2C%20its%20top%20leadership%20said%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20R.K%20Meghan%2C%20an%20ideologue%20of%20UNLF%20freed%20by%20the%20government%20in%202019%20from%20Guwahati%20jail%20and%20now%20residing%20in%20Imphal%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Frk-meghan-rebel-leader-manipur-arrives-imphal%5C%22%3Estaying%20away%20from%20the%20latest%20%E2%80%98ceasefire%20move%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20further%20points%20to%20the%20gulf.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAny%20compulsion%20on%20the%20Pambei%20faction%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20cadres%20of%20the%20Koireng%20faction%20are%20currently%20located%20beyond%20the%20international%20border%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20Pambei%E2%80%99s%20men%20are%20said%20to%20have%20slipped%20into%20Manipur%20during%20the%20recent%20ethnic%20strife%20of%20the%20Meiteis%20with%20the%20Kuki%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20been%20allegations%20of%20valley-based%20militant%20groups%2C%20including%20UNLF%2C%20participating%20in%20the%20recent%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthefrontiermanipur.com%2Funlf-under-leadership-of-chairman-kh-pambei-decides-to-sign-ceasefire-pact-with-goi-for-onward-political-negotiation%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Frontier%20Manipur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20November%2028%20on%20the%20Pambei%20faction%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20the%20government%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20party%20(Thanil)%20states%20(at%20the%20raising%20Day)%20that%20after%20an%20understanding%20was%20reached%20between%20authorities%20representing%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20UNLF%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Chairman%20Kh%20Pambei%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20decided%20not%20to%20act%20against%20each%20other.%20This%20is%20probably%20why%20central%20and%20state%20armed%20forces%20were%20not%20acting%20against%20them%20even%20as%20UNLF%20still%20remains%20a%20proscribed%20armed%20group.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-govt-allocates-rs-5-crore-as-sexual-violence-compensation-no-info-on-how-many-to-receive-it%5C%22%3EManipur%20Govt%20Allocates%20Rs%205-Crore%20as%20Sexual%20Violence%20Compensation%2C%20No%20Info%20on%20How%20Many%20to%20Receive%20It%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20this%20is%20the%20truth%2C%20then%20what%20is%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Pambei%20group%E2%80%99s%20mind%20is%20to%20trade%20with%20Delhi%20for%20a%20cover%20for%20its%20cadres%20who%20are%20already%20in%20Imphal.%20Security%20forces%20have%20already%20gone%20after%20the%20cadres%20of%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20of%20Manipur%20(PLA)%20and%20some%20other%20valley-based%20armed%20outfits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20militants%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20ban%20on%20their%20outfits%2C%20could%20openly%20operate%20in%20the%20valley%20areas%20during%20the%20ethnic%20strife%20also%20because%2C%20unlike%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Manipur%2C%20the%20security%20forces%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20extra%20powers%20under%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20(Special%20Powers)%20Act%20(AFSPA)%20anymore.%20On%20one%20occasion%2C%20security%20forces%20had%20to%20release%20some%20militants%20belonging%20to%20a%20proscribed%20group%20due%20to%20public%20pressure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20relenting%20to%20the%20longstanding%20demand%20of%20the%20Meiteis%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20AFSPA%20from%20the%20valley%20areas%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20dithering%20now%20to%20bring%20back%20any%20stringent%20law%20particularly%20when%20it%20had%20gone%20to%20town%20as%20a%20proof%20of%20%E2%80%98peace%E2%80%99%20in%20Manipur.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMedia%20shut-down%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20needs%20holding%20up%20here%20is%20also%20the%20voluntary%20%E2%80%98shut-down%E2%80%99%20of%20sorts%20by%20the%20valley-based%20media%20organisations%20at%20a%20time%20when%20UNLF%20was%20set%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20New%20Delhi.%20According%20to%20local%20journalists%2C%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20by%20media%20groups%20%E2%80%9Cto%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20barrage%20of%20statements%20issued%20by%20both%20the%20factions%20of%20UNLF%20justifying%20their%20positions%20to%20the%20public%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20print%20versions%20of%20local%20newspapers%20have%20begun%20publishing%20only%20four%20days%20ago%2C%20their%20online%20versions%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20the%20report%20of%20UNLF%E2%80%99s%20ceasefire%20talks%20with%20the%20Union%20till%20a%20day%20ago.%20The%20only%20exception%20was%2C%20the%20online%20news%20outfit%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Frontier%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20uneasiness%20of%20the%20local%20media%20to%20function%20independently%20was%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20national%20media%20was%20awash%20with%20news%20about%20%E2%80%98UNLF%20ceasefire%E2%80%99%20in%20Manipur%20by%20Shah.%20Biren%20arrived%20at%20the%20Imphal%20airport%20on%20December%201%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98hero%E2%80%99s%20welcome%E2%80%99%20only%20by%20his%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20colleagues.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20continue%20UNLF%20ban%20during%20ceasefire%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20ceasefire%20has%20been%20lauded%20by%20the%20Union%20and%20Biren%20government%20as%20arrival%20of%20peace%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20MHA%20has%20not%20lifted%20the%20ban%20on%20UNLF%2C%20a%20first%20in%20any%20North-East%20peace%20initiative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ban%20on%20NSCN%20(Issac-Muivah)%20was%20lifted%20in%20Nagaland%20when%20the%20Union%20had%20entered%20into%20a%20ceasefire%20agreement%20with%20it.%20Ditto%20with%20the%20United%20Liberation%20Front%20of%20Asom%20(ULFA).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20only%20a%20faction%20of%20UNLF%20ready%20to%20join%20the%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20lifting%20of%20the%20ban%20is%20clearly%20not%20feasible%20at%20the%20moment.%20To%20stem%20the%20question%20though%2C%20the%20MHA%20has%20formed%20a%20tribunal%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20to%20adjudicate%20whether%20there%20is%20sufficient%20reason%20for%20its%20renewal%20of%20the%20ban%20this%20past%20November%2013%20on%20not%20just%20the%20UNLF%20but%20seven%20other%20valley-based%20armed%20groups.%20The%20tribunal%20is%20to%20be%20headed%20by%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Medhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20such%20tribunal%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20hence%20the%20move%20comes%20across%20only%20as%20a%20palliative%20of%20sorts%20by%20Delhi%20for%20the%20majority%20community%20which%20has%20been%20upset%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20for%20not%20even%20visiting%20them%20during%20the%20recent%20violence.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701499168000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02120041%2FGAQUezCWwAAHb9J.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipurs-ceasefire-agreement-explained%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20reality%20is%20that%20only%20a%20faction%20of%20the%20UNLF%20has%20participated%20in%20the%20peace%20talks%20%E2%80%93%20much%20smaller%20in%20terms%20of%20cadre%20capacity%20than%20the%20one%20that%20has%20decided%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20latest%20%E2%80%98ceasefire%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20government.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipurs-ceasefire-agreement-explained%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bologna's%20leaning%20tower%20sealed%20off%20over%20fears%20it%20could%20collapse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701497182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F16026%2Fproduction%2F_131905109_gettyimages-1186113140.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67599067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Work%20has%20begun%20on%20a%20barrier%20around%20the%20Garisenda%20Tower%20and%20authorities%20say%20the%20situation%20is%20%26quot%3Bcritical%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A793%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67599067%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67599067.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67599067.amp%2